Dialogue: 0,0:31:33.57,0:31:35.02,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:35.02,0:31:41.79,Default,,0,0,0,,As you will.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:41.79,0:31:47.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, you wrote a book about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:47.53,0:31:50.53,Default,,0,0,0,,You got every kind of a humorous book you could find.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:50.53,0:31:56.90,Default,,0,0,0,,And he just kept laughing all the time and eventually it cured it.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:56.90,0:32:00.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Norman Cousins?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:00.75,0:32:03.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, I wanted it for your reference.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:03.75,0:32:06.03,Default,,0,0,0,,That's sufficient.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:06.03,0:32:08.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:08.50,0:32:11.98,Default,,0,0,0,,God bless.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:11.98,0:32:12.98,Default,,0,0,0,,God bless.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:12.98,0:32:16.28,Default,,0,0,0,,God bless you.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:16.28,0:32:17.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Amen.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:17.28,0:32:36.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Norman Cousins, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:36.66,0:32:38.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I couldn't think of the name at the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:38.66,0:32:40.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:40.94,0:33:01.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Howdy.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:01.81,0:33:05.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm nervous.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:05.74,0:33:08.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I just simply wanted to do something that my ego didn't want.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:08.74,0:33:09.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Want me to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:09.74,0:33:12.76,Default,,0,0,0,,May I just touch your feet and ask for a blessing?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:12.76,0:33:13.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:13.76,0:33:16.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Easy question.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:18.20,0:33:20.20,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll put that in the donation basket.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:20.20,0:33:21.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:21.20,0:33:22.20,Default,,0,0,0,,God bless you.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:22.20,0:33:25.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:25.11,0:33:26.11,Default,,0,0,0,,God bless you.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:26.11,0:33:31.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Put this with donations.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:31.59,0:33:32.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Right here.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:32.59,0:33:35.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Give it to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:35.71,0:33:36.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Otherwise I'll lose it.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:36.71,0:33:37.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello, Dr. Hawkins.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:37.71,0:33:55.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:55.99,0:33:56.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't have a question either.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:56.99,0:34:06.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I just wanted to take a moment to express my gratitude to you and your teachings and
Dialogue: 0,0:34:06.50,0:34:10.57,Default,,0,0,0,,let you know that they've really helped me find God in my life.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:10.57,0:34:15.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm just so grateful that I could be here today to feel your energy.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:15.57,0:34:18.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I thank you and ask for your blessing.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:18.69,0:34:20.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for thanking me.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:20.69,0:34:22.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:22.21,0:34:45.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello, Dr. Hawkins.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:45.13,0:34:51.13,Default,,0,0,0,,A few years ago, I was briefly under the influence of a false guru.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:51.13,0:34:54.13,Default,,0,0,0,,When I came out of it a couple of weeks later, I started hearing voices.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:54.13,0:34:58.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I believed that I was being counseled by the white brotherhood.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:58.13,0:35:02.13,Default,,0,0,0,,It took several months before I realized the error I made and refused to listen anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:02.13,0:35:03.13,Default,,0,0,0,,It took—wait a minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:03.13,0:35:04.13,Default,,0,0,0,,You're going too fast.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:04.13,0:35:05.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:05.13,0:35:11.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I was under the influence of what I thought was the white brotherhood, but I think from
Dialogue: 0,0:35:11.34,0:35:14.34,Default,,0,0,0,,reading your books that it was actually astral entities.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:14.34,0:35:15.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:15.34,0:35:16.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:16.34,0:35:18.34,Default,,0,0,0,,It keeps coming up again and again, and I wondered if there's something that needs
Dialogue: 0,0:35:18.34,0:35:21.34,Default,,0,0,0,,to be cleared from my aura or something I need to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:21.34,0:35:23.34,Default,,0,0,0,,What's coming up again and again?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:23.34,0:35:28.46,Default,,0,0,0,,For several months, I was under the influence.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:28.46,0:35:33.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I was directed to do things, told to do things, and I thought that I was working in the service
Dialogue: 0,0:35:33.46,0:35:35.46,Default,,0,0,0,,of God, but I wasn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:35.46,0:35:36.46,Default,,0,0,0,,How did you get here?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:36.46,0:35:37.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you hear these?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:37.46,0:35:39.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Was it auditory or what?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:39.46,0:35:45.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Messages would appear in my mind, and initially, they were written down.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:45.46,0:35:48.46,Default,,0,0,0,,They told me—I thought I was mad.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:48.46,0:35:50.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought I was making it up.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:50.46,0:35:54.46,Default,,0,0,0,,But several of the things that occurred, I later found out through your readings, were
Dialogue: 0,0:35:54.46,0:35:57.82,Default,,0,0,0,,actually true.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:57.82,0:36:04.17,Default,,0,0,0,,It was a difficult period, and I don't know how else to explain it.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:04.17,0:36:09.17,Default,,0,0,0,,But I've heard you say before that if you've been involved with astral entities, that you
Dialogue: 0,0:36:09.17,0:36:11.17,Default,,0,0,0,,have to have your aura cleared.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:11.17,0:36:15.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, if that makes you happy, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:15.42,0:36:19.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:19.36,0:36:25.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I followed the guidance I was given, and I seem to be all right, but I keep worrying
Dialogue: 0,0:36:25.36,0:36:27.36,Default,,0,0,0,,about it, which is why I'm here.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:27.36,0:36:30.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, you grow beyond it.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:30.36,0:36:31.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Just—
Dialogue: 0,0:36:31.36,0:36:33.36,Default,,0,0,0,,These things come in phases.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:33.36,0:36:37.36,Default,,0,0,0,,There'll be a couple of years where all kinds of weird things happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:37.36,0:36:42.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Then there'll be a year or two where weird gurus show up out of the woodwork, you know,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:42.36,0:36:47.36,Default,,0,0,0,,and say, bonky, bonky.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:47.36,0:36:51.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Stick to the tried and true.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:51.67,0:36:53.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, I know that now.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:53.67,0:36:54.67,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:54.67,0:37:00.67,Default,,0,0,0,,In books I've written, we calibrate the level of spiritual teachers.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:00.67,0:37:01.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:01.67,0:37:04.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Pick one that appeals to you and follow it strictly.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:04.67,0:37:08.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:08.40,0:37:10.40,Default,,0,0,0,,And eventually it'll go away.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:10.40,0:37:11.40,Default,,0,0,0,,It'll go away.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:11.40,0:37:12.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:12.40,0:37:13.40,Default,,0,0,0,,So I don't have to worry about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:13.40,0:37:14.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, it'll go away.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:14.42,0:37:15.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:15.42,0:37:18.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:18.38,0:37:19.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:19.38,0:37:29.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, Susan.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:29.46,0:37:30.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello, Dr. Hawkins.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:30.46,0:37:31.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:31.46,0:37:32.46,Default,,0,0,0,,It's very nice to be here.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:32.46,0:37:40.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I see light in dark things or energies, and I need help in knowing what they are, and
Dialogue: 0,0:37:40.46,0:37:43.46,Default,,0,0,0,,is it necessary that I do know what they are?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:43.46,0:37:45.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Lights in what?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:45.42,0:37:46.42,Default,,0,0,0,,In what?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:46.42,0:37:48.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Is this light up here?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:48.23,0:37:49.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:49.23,0:37:54.46,Default,,0,0,0,,No, like light and dark things in the, I guess the atmosphere.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:54.46,0:37:56.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Are they tiny or large?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:56.46,0:37:59.46,Default,,0,0,0,,They can be tiny and they can be large.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:59.46,0:38:02.46,Default,,0,0,0,,They can be bright white lights popping around.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:02.46,0:38:06.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Sometimes they're wispy and then sometimes they're dark.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:06.34,0:38:08.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Sometimes they will appear around people.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:08.34,0:38:09.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:09.34,0:38:17.23,Default,,0,0,0,,And depending on the situation that I'm in or the group, they can be more so, more present
Dialogue: 0,0:38:17.23,0:38:18.23,Default,,0,0,0,,than others.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:18.23,0:38:20.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:20.26,0:38:22.26,Default,,0,0,0,,And I'm not for sure exactly what they are.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:22.26,0:38:28.71,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not modified by anything you're doing or saying or state you're in?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:28.71,0:38:29.80,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:29.80,0:38:30.80,Default,,0,0,0,,They come and go of their own?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:30.80,0:38:31.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:31.80,0:38:33.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Do they seem to have a message?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:33.80,0:38:42.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Sometimes if I ask questions in my mind, they will happen to appear more quickly.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:42.01,0:38:45.42,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you think they are?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:45.42,0:38:48.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Angels.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:48.92,0:38:50.92,Default,,0,0,0,,What she's seeing is angels resist.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:50.92,0:38:54.94,Default,,0,0,0,,What she's seeing is phosphenes resist.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:54.94,0:38:56.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:56.13,0:39:04.71,Default,,0,0,0,,You're seeing little illuminations that are concomitant to the neuronal activity of the
Dialogue: 0,0:39:04.71,0:39:05.71,Default,,0,0,0,,brain's neurons.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:05.71,0:39:07.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh-huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:07.80,0:39:08.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:08.80,0:39:11.80,Default,,0,0,0,,So just accept that it's normal and enjoy them.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:11.80,0:39:13.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Just accept it's normal.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:13.96,0:39:19.00,Default,,0,0,0,,If I close my eyes right now, there's a million tiny specks of light.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:19.00,0:39:22.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:22.23,0:39:26.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Because they're there all the time, I don't pay attention to them.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:26.84,0:39:27.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I just ignore them.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:27.84,0:39:29.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:29.32,0:39:30.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:30.32,0:39:31.32,Default,,0,0,0,,And one more.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:31.32,0:39:32.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Would you come to Nashville and speak?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:32.32,0:39:33.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:33.32,0:39:34.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:34.32,0:39:35.32,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:35.32,0:39:36.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I've got a question about time.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:36.32,0:39:43.59,Default,,0,0,0,,You talk about time and you talk today about getting older.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:43.59,0:39:44.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:44.59,0:39:45.59,Default,,0,0,0,,But then sometimes you talk about how there's no such thing as time.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:45.59,0:39:46.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:46.88,0:39:47.88,Default,,0,0,0,,That it's a superimposition upon phenomena that are happening simultaneously.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:47.88,0:39:48.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:48.88,0:39:49.88,Default,,0,0,0,,You're mixing levels of truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:49.88,0:39:50.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:50.88,0:39:51.92,Default,,0,0,0,,You're mixing levels.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:51.92,0:39:52.92,Default,,0,0,0,,So what do you do?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:52.92,0:39:53.92,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you do?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:53.92,0:39:54.92,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you do?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:54.92,0:39:55.92,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you do?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:55.92,0:39:56.92,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you do?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:56.92,0:39:57.92,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you do?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:57.92,0:39:58.92,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you do?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:58.92,0:39:59.92,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you do?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:59.92,0:40:00.92,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you do?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:00.92,0:40:03.57,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you do?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:03.57,0:40:04.57,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you do?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:04.57,0:40:05.57,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you do?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:05.57,0:40:06.57,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you do?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:06.57,0:40:09.34,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you do?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:09.34,0:40:10.34,Default,,0,0,0,,What.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:10.34,0:40:13.78,Default,,0,0,0,,So what, well that's, I guess that's because I can't figure it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:13.78,0:40:18.01,Default,,0,0,0,,What, there's no such thing as time, but we see ourselves growing older.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:18.01,0:40:19.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:19.01,0:40:20.01,Default,,0,0,0,,But is it.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:20.01,0:40:21.01,Default,,0,0,0,,We call that time.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:21.01,0:40:22.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, we call it time.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:22.01,0:40:26.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it because if you try to figure out time over all of the universe you can't do that
Dialogue: 0,0:40:26.88,0:40:29.90,Default,,0,0,0,,because of multiple dimensions?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:29.90,0:40:35.34,Default,,0,0,0,,But could time be local for purpose?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:35.34,0:40:37.80,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you want to know this for?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:37.80,0:40:38.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I was just, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:38.80,0:40:39.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I just wondered about.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:39.80,0:40:40.30,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't have any reason to know it.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:40.30,0:40:40.40,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a connection.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:40.40,0:40:40.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:40.51,0:40:42.57,Default,,0,0,0,,you've made up to confuse yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:42.57,0:40:43.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:43.57,0:40:45.42,Default,,0,0,0,,The answers to it are very,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:45.42,0:40:49.34,Default,,0,0,0,,the actual answers to it are in advanced quantum mechanics
Dialogue: 0,0:40:49.34,0:40:51.92,Default,,0,0,0,,and advanced theoretical physics.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:51.92,0:40:55.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Whether time is limited to a certain dimension,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:55.98,0:40:58.38,Default,,0,0,0,,whether it's all-inclusive,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:58.38,0:41:02.63,Default,,0,0,0,,whether there's forward time and backward time.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:02.63,0:41:07.46,Default,,0,0,0,,It's, to me, games people play with
Dialogue: 0,0:41:07.46,0:41:09.40,Default,,0,0,0,,in advanced theoretical physics
Dialogue: 0,0:41:09.40,0:41:12.65,Default,,0,0,0,,with no actual application to their life at all, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:12.65,0:41:13.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:13.76,0:41:15.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you gonna stop making love because of it,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:15.48,0:41:18.26,Default,,0,0,0,,or are you gonna eat nothing but grapefruit,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:18.26,0:41:20.28,Default,,0,0,0,,or, I mean, you know what I mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:20.28,0:41:23.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess when you say there's no such thing as time,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:23.25,0:41:25.28,Default,,0,0,0,,but then you say don't waste time.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:25.28,0:41:26.65,Default,,0,0,0,,It's you referring to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:26.65,0:41:27.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I was just trying to figure out.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:27.48,0:41:31.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, but we're talking about different contextualizations.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:31.53,0:41:34.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:34.17,0:41:35.76,Default,,0,0,0,,What you see is sequence.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:35.76,0:41:41.30,Default,,0,0,0,,That sequence is delineated as time, measurable time.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:41.42,0:41:42.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:42.65,0:41:46.23,Default,,0,0,0,,And then beyond that is the timeless.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:46.23,0:41:51.00,Default,,0,0,0,,So time is like a subdivision underneath,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:51.00,0:41:54.92,Default,,0,0,0,,let's say, the sky, you know what I'm saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:54.92,0:41:57.92,Default,,0,0,0,,How big is the sky?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:57.92,0:41:59.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, it's as big as you want to define it,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:59.84,0:42:01.46,Default,,0,0,0,,you know what I'm saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:01.46,0:42:04.88,Default,,0,0,0,,It doesn't, there isn't any beginning of the sky
Dialogue: 0,0:42:04.88,0:42:06.44,Default,,0,0,0,,and ending of the sky.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:10.05,0:42:14.42,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a point of observation.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:14.42,0:42:15.17,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:15.17,0:42:16.13,Default,,0,0,0,,The actual,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:16.13,0:42:19.40,Default,,0,0,0,,the actual fulfillment of this understanding,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:19.40,0:42:24.40,Default,,0,0,0,,you could try whatchamacallit, mindful universe.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:25.34,0:42:26.44,Default,,0,0,0,,You read that?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:26.44,0:42:27.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I've heard of it, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:27.98,0:42:29.92,Default,,0,0,0,,No, you gotta read it, not heard of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:31.92,0:42:33.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:33.28,0:42:35.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Mindful universe is a good place to start.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:35.38,0:42:36.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:36.67,0:42:38.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Professor of physics at Berkeley.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:38.53,0:42:39.86,Default,,0,0,0,,It's readable.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:39.86,0:42:41.38,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:41.38,0:42:53.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I'm just gonna do what's humanly possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:57.13,0:42:58.13,Default,,0,0,0,,.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:00.59,0:43:01.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that writing?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:01.09,0:43:05.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't tell if it's writing or not.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:05.59,0:43:07.78,Default,,0,0,0,,No, this pen's dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:07.78,0:43:14.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know, you can't get a pen that, yeah, unbelievable.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:14.63,0:43:19.44,Default,,0,0,0,,.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:19.44,0:43:21.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Here, I'll use this one.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:21.80,0:43:23.05,Default,,0,0,0,,There was another one laying here.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:23.05,0:43:24.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't have it today.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:24.44,0:43:29.26,Default,,0,0,0,,There's another pen there.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:29.26,0:43:32.94,Default,,0,0,0,,This pen doesn't write at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:32.94,0:43:40.42,Default,,0,0,0,,.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:40.42,0:43:41.86,Default,,0,0,0,,You got three for the price of one.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:41.86,0:43:42.78,Default,,0,0,0,,You've got a lot of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:42.78,0:43:45.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know, I don't know what to do with this.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:45.69,0:43:49.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Endless requests.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:49.30,0:43:50.65,Default,,0,0,0,,That's better.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:50.65,0:43:51.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Yep. They bring you books.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:51.69,0:43:53.78,Default,,0,0,0,,They bring you a book with no pen.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:53.78,0:43:56.19,Default,,0,0,0,,.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:56.19,0:43:57.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:57.19,0:43:58.36,Default,,0,0,0,,.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:58.36,0:43:59.36,Default,,0,0,0,,How many of these?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:59.36,0:44:00.36,Default,,0,0,0,,What does this thing say?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:00.36,0:44:01.36,Default,,0,0,0,,It's for everybody back in the day.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:01.36,0:44:02.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I see, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:02.36,0:44:04.05,Default,,0,0,0,,.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:04.05,0:44:07.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I just firstly wanted to say thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:07.05,0:44:09.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't possibly say that enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:09.05,0:44:12.67,Default,,0,0,0,,.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:12.67,0:44:13.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:13.67,0:44:14.90,Default,,0,0,0,,.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:14.90,0:44:21.90,Default,,0,0,0,,My question is, we have a study group back in Maryland, and we help each other through testing different situations in our life.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:21.90,0:44:22.90,Default,,0,0,0,,.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:22.90,0:44:26.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't sign all these.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:26.17,0:44:27.17,Default,,0,0,0,,That's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:27.17,0:44:36.26,Default,,0,0,0,,.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:36.26,0:44:39.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:39.82,0:44:40.82,Default,,0,0,0,,.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:40.82,0:44:50.01,Default,,0,0,0,,So my question is, we test through the situations in our life, and sometimes we test, is this a karmic issue, and we actually get no.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:50.01,0:44:54.01,Default,,0,0,0,,But from what I've learned, everything is, we are our karma.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:54.01,0:44:56.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Our karma is everything that's happened to us.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:56.51,0:45:00.51,Default,,0,0,0,,So how can we test that the situation is not related to our karma?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:00.51,0:45:01.51,Default,,0,0,0,,.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:01.51,0:45:04.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Sometimes what you mean by karma is historic karma.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:04.51,0:45:06.61,Default,,0,0,0,,.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:06.61,0:45:08.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:08.86,0:45:09.86,Default,,0,0,0,,.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:09.86,0:45:11.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Everything is karma, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:11.65,0:45:16.65,Default,,0,0,0,,What generally people mean is historic karma, past lives and past decisions.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:16.65,0:45:18.38,Default,,0,0,0,,.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:18.38,0:45:21.38,Default,,0,0,0,,So when we ask the question if it's related to our karma, then that is our. .
Dialogue: 0,0:45:21.38,0:45:22.38,Default,,0,0,0,,When you ask what question?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:22.38,0:45:23.38,Default,,0,0,0,,.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:23.38,0:45:28.38,Default,,0,0,0,,If we ask if it is a karmic issue, then we are implicitly asking from a previous life, not this one.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:28.38,0:45:29.38,Default,,0,0,0,,.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:29.38,0:45:30.38,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what you're really asking, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:30.38,0:45:32.90,Default,,0,0,0,,.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:32.90,0:45:33.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:33.90,0:45:47.73,Default,,0,0,0,,.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:47.73,0:45:57.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Is this a pen?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:57.59,0:45:58.59,Default,,0,0,0,,.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:58.59,0:45:59.59,Default,,0,0,0,,No, it's a pen.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:59.59,0:46:11.21,Default,,0,0,0,,.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:11.21,0:46:12.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:12.21,0:46:13.21,Default,,0,0,0,,.
