Dialogue: 0,0:47:23.82,0:47:24.82,Default,,0,0,0,,.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:24.82,0:47:25.82,Default,,0,0,0,,.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:25.82,0:47:26.82,Default,,0,0,0,,.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:26.82,0:47:27.82,Default,,0,0,0,,.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:27.82,0:47:28.82,Default,,0,0,0,,.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:28.82,0:47:29.82,Default,,0,0,0,,.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:29.82,0:47:30.82,Default,,0,0,0,,.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:30.82,0:47:31.82,Default,,0,0,0,,.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:31.82,0:47:32.82,Default,,0,0,0,,.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:32.82,0:47:36.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it for the highest good that she moves to the U.S.?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:36.30,0:47:37.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, let's ask.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:37.71,0:47:39.61,Default,,0,0,0,,We have permission to ask this.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:41.07,0:47:44.40,Default,,0,0,0,,It would serve her highest good to move to the U.S., resist.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:45.92,0:47:47.07,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the answer we got.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:47.76,0:47:49.61,Default,,0,0,0,,And the second one was,
Dialogue: 0,0:47:50.40,0:47:53.84,Default,,0,0,0,,it is for the highest good that I remain in Luxembourg,
Dialogue: 0,0:47:53.96,0:47:55.01,Default,,0,0,0,,where I currently live.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:01.09,0:48:07.38,Default,,0,0,0,,But I guess that's redundant because the first one is yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:07.38,0:48:08.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's see.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:08.86,0:48:11.19,Default,,0,0,0,,It would serve her highest good to move to the United States.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:11.48,0:48:11.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:11.98,0:48:14.38,Default,,0,0,0,,But it's also okay that she stay in Luxembourg.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:15.36,0:48:16.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Either one.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:16.71,0:48:21.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, thank you, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:22.59,0:48:24.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Why is there such a profusion of these?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:24.55,0:48:27.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Because it's for the whole study group, so you have to do this.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:27.71,0:48:28.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:29.19,0:48:30.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I see, okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:30.48,0:48:31.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, all right, okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:33.88,0:48:36.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, those were the only two statements that I had.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:36.96,0:48:37.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:38.21,0:48:38.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you both.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:39.38,0:48:40.36,Default,,0,0,0,,It's either way, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:40.36,0:48:41.67,Default,,0,0,0,,It's okay either way, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:41.82,0:48:43.94,Default,,0,0,0,,But it's been a dilemma for three years,
Dialogue: 0,0:48:44.15,0:48:46.78,Default,,0,0,0,,and each time I ask myself what I should do,
Dialogue: 0,0:48:47.17,0:48:49.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I keep thinking that I'm listening to my ego.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:49.61,0:48:51.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, so why don't you ask for guidance?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:52.40,0:48:53.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I've done that too.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:53.98,0:48:57.94,Default,,0,0,0,,And then I thought that the only possible answer I had
Dialogue: 0,0:48:57.94,0:49:00.46,Default,,0,0,0,,was to come here and ask you to calibrate that.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:00.90,0:49:02.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe that's why you're not getting the answers.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:02.57,0:49:03.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Either one is all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:03.84,0:49:04.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, it could be that.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:05.26,0:49:05.82,Default,,0,0,0,,It could be that.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:06.92,0:49:09.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, it sounds like it's come see, come saw.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:10.00,0:49:10.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Either or.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:10.73,0:49:11.80,Default,,0,0,0,,You speak French.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:12.07,0:49:12.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Fantastic.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:16.17,0:49:16.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Merci beaucoup.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:17.46,0:49:18.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:22.94,0:49:23.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:37.50,0:49:38.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, you bet.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:41.34,0:49:42.48,Default,,0,0,0,,That's a profusion.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:45.46,0:49:46.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know whose pens these are.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:48.26,0:49:48.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:48.84,0:49:50.19,Default,,0,0,0,,We can look at everybody's pens.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:51.94,0:49:52.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:55.98,0:49:58.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I just wanted to thank you for being my teacher
Dialogue: 0,0:49:58.30,0:50:02.84,Default,,0,0,0,,and for saving me lifetimes and lifetimes
Dialogue: 0,0:50:02.84,0:50:04.65,Default,,0,0,0,,of inquiry and reading.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:06.53,0:50:07.84,Default,,0,0,0,,And my...
Dialogue: 0,0:50:08.69,0:50:12.30,Default,,0,0,0,,My inner song is happy, and my outer song is happy too.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:12.80,0:50:13.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Good, good, good.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:14.01,0:50:14.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:16.07,0:50:20.73,Default,,0,0,0,,She sounds happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:36.32,0:50:36.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:38.75,0:50:39.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi, Dr. Hawkins.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:39.94,0:50:42.09,Default,,0,0,0,,First of all, it's just a pleasure to be here
Dialogue: 0,0:50:42.09,0:50:43.07,Default,,0,0,0,,and to be in your presence
Dialogue: 0,0:50:43.07,0:50:45.92,Default,,0,0,0,,and to be able to be around someone
Dialogue: 0,0:50:45.92,0:50:47.63,Default,,0,0,0,,that's given so much to humanity.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:48.36,0:50:50.71,Default,,0,0,0,,And I thank you as well as I know all of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:50.80,0:50:51.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for that.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:52.36,0:50:53.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I have a question.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:53.53,0:50:55.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been studying A Course in Miracles
Dialogue: 0,0:50:55.03,0:50:57.57,Default,,0,0,0,,and as well as your teachings for about the past eight years.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:57.67,0:50:58.38,Default,,0,0,0,,And through this,
Dialogue: 0,0:50:58.44,0:50:59.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I've gone through a lot of
Dialogue: 0,0:50:59.67,0:51:02.25,Default,,0,0,0,,what feels like an undoing process.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:03.36,0:51:04.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I've gotten to a point now
Dialogue: 0,0:51:04.82,0:51:06.73,Default,,0,0,0,,where it feels as if I'm at a place
Dialogue: 0,0:51:06.73,0:51:10.21,Default,,0,0,0,,where I almost have had experiences
Dialogue: 0,0:51:10.21,0:51:12.34,Default,,0,0,0,,where I felt I had to surrender my existence,
Dialogue: 0,0:51:12.73,0:51:13.42,Default,,0,0,0,,like my...
Dialogue: 0,0:51:13.42,0:51:15.94,Default,,0,0,0,,like not my existence, but existence itself.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:16.32,0:51:18.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I felt I had to surrender that.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:19.13,0:51:21.57,Default,,0,0,0,,And it was too scary for me to go through.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:21.96,0:51:25.80,Default,,0,0,0,,And I felt like I was being sucked into a vortex.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:25.80,0:51:26.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:26.88,0:51:28.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Of energy that I would...
Dialogue: 0,0:51:28.51,0:51:30.07,Default,,0,0,0,,You'd never be able to come back out of
Dialogue: 0,0:51:30.07,0:51:31.38,Default,,0,0,0,,once you make it through there.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:31.48,0:51:32.63,Default,,0,0,0,,And it was too scary.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:32.86,0:51:34.63,Default,,0,0,0,,And the couple times when this has come up,
Dialogue: 0,0:51:34.76,0:51:37.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I've pulled out of it because of fear.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:37.92,0:51:40.32,Default,,0,0,0,,And I wonder if you could tell me
Dialogue: 0,0:51:40.32,0:51:43.65,Default,,0,0,0,,if you think that's safe to do that
Dialogue: 0,0:51:43.65,0:51:44.53,Default,,0,0,0,,or if my instincts...
Dialogue: 0,0:51:44.53,0:51:45.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I've walked through that door
Dialogue: 0,0:51:45.63,0:51:47.09,Default,,0,0,0,,and I've described that door.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:47.61,0:51:49.23,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why I came here to ask you this.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:51.17,0:51:52.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I've described that door.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:55.42,0:51:57.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Did it feel like demons were pulling at you?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:57.65,0:51:58.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, did it feel demonic?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:58.69,0:51:58.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Like what?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:58.86,0:52:00.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Like fearful and demonic and...
Dialogue: 0,0:52:01.78,0:52:02.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Was it scary?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:04.07,0:52:04.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Terrifying.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:07.36,0:52:09.42,Default,,0,0,0,,It's safe for her to surrender
Dialogue: 0,0:52:09.42,0:52:11.28,Default,,0,0,0,,what she's contemplating surrendering.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:13.34,0:52:14.73,Default,,0,0,0,,All fear is illusion.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:19.11,0:52:19.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:19.92,0:52:21.78,Default,,0,0,0,,And I'd like to ask
Dialogue: 0,0:52:21.78,0:52:24.78,Default,,0,0,0,,if you could calibrate an organization for me
Dialogue: 0,0:52:24.78,0:52:26.67,Default,,0,0,0,,that I've considered joining,
Dialogue: 0,0:52:27.30,0:52:29.00,Default,,0,0,0,,if it would be in the highest and best good
Dialogue: 0,0:52:29.00,0:52:30.92,Default,,0,0,0,,of the service to humanity
Dialogue: 0,0:52:30.92,0:52:32.98,Default,,0,0,0,,for me to join this organization.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:33.19,0:52:33.48,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:33.51,0:52:35.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Just hold the organization in your mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:35.51,0:52:36.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't want to know the name of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:37.78,0:52:38.05,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:38.05,0:52:39.65,Default,,0,0,0,,We have permission to ask this.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:41.11,0:52:42.80,Default,,0,0,0,,In the name of the highest good,
Dialogue: 0,0:52:42.92,0:52:45.19,Default,,0,0,0,,the organization that she wants to join
Dialogue: 0,0:52:45.19,0:52:48.19,Default,,0,0,0,,is ethical and of the highest order.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:48.53,0:52:48.78,Default,,0,0,0,,What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:50.40,0:52:53.15,Default,,0,0,0,,It is not of the highest order.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:56.03,0:52:56.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:01.51,0:53:01.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:16.21,0:53:18.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I wanted to ask if you would bless my wee ones,
Dialogue: 0,0:53:18.42,0:53:19.21,Default,,0,0,0,,especially Keiko.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:19.98,0:53:20.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:20.44,0:53:20.61,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:20.69,0:53:23.09,Default,,0,0,0,,These are her little sugar babies.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:23.61,0:53:27.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, God bless you, cute little boogers.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:27.19,0:53:28.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Are those for dinner tonight?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:30.98,0:53:32.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Are we having them for dinner?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:35.50,0:53:36.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Susan, there are seven.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:40.13,0:53:42.63,Default,,0,0,0,,There are seven sugar babies that are just wonderful.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:43.48,0:53:45.03,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll have to take one out and show everyone
Dialogue: 0,0:53:45.03,0:53:46.09,Default,,0,0,0,,because they're just adorable.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:46.09,0:53:46.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:46.11,0:53:47.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I love these things.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:47.34,0:53:47.48,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:47.48,0:53:48.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Take one out now?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:48.17,0:53:49.92,Default,,0,0,0,,If you can't eat it, we'll go to the...
Dialogue: 0,0:53:50.51,0:53:50.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:50.80,0:53:53.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Pick out one that's going to be to a man, get to a man.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:57.09,0:53:57.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Yep.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:01.30,0:54:02.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Teeny wincy.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:02.67,0:54:03.88,Default,,0,0,0,,They don't like the light.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:03.98,0:54:06.98,Default,,0,0,0,,They're nocturnal, so they don't like this much light.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:07.88,0:54:08.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:08.69,0:54:09.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:09.01,0:54:09.59,Default,,0,0,0,,God bless you.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:10.07,0:54:10.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Bless you.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:10.32,0:54:10.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:10.92,0:54:11.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:11.55,0:54:11.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:11.94,0:54:12.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:12.51,0:54:13.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Appreciate you.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:13.51,0:54:13.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:13.98,0:54:14.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:14.75,0:54:15.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:16.46,0:54:16.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:18.19,0:54:19.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing more fun than pets.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:21.96,0:54:22.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:28.98,0:54:29.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Great teacher.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:29.63,0:54:32.65,Default,,0,0,0,,My question is simple.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:32.90,0:54:36.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Is enlightenment basically easy or is it difficult?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:39.11,0:54:42.38,Default,,0,0,0,,It only takes a couple dozen lifetimes.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:44.03,0:54:44.38,Default,,0,0,0,,At minimum?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:46.82,0:54:48.23,Default,,0,0,0,,This is my basic question.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:49.40,0:54:52.92,Default,,0,0,0,,That's kind of oversimplified, but is it a simpler truth?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:53.21,0:54:54.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Do we make it difficult?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:54.34,0:54:54.48,Default,,0,0,0,,By simply saying, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:54.51,0:54:58.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Are we just striving for it and thinking about it and trying to get there, or is it ...
Dialogue: 0,0:54:58.44,0:55:03.75,Default,,0,0,0,,It's difficult, and it's because we're making it difficult, but it's difficult to let go
Dialogue: 0,0:55:03.75,0:55:04.75,Default,,0,0,0,,of making it difficult.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:04.75,0:55:07.76,Default,,0,0,0,,It makes perfect sense.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:07.76,0:55:08.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:08.76,0:55:09.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi, Dr. Hawkins.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:09.76,0:55:10.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't have a question.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:10.76,0:55:12.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I just wanted to draw near and just sit in your presence and hopefully just hold your
Dialogue: 0,0:55:12.11,0:55:13.11,Default,,0,0,0,,hand just for a few seconds.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:13.11,0:55:22.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:22.88,0:55:23.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:23.88,0:55:24.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:24.88,0:55:25.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:25.88,0:55:26.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:26.88,0:55:27.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:27.88,0:55:28.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:28.94,0:55:29.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:29.94,0:55:30.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:30.94,0:55:31.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:31.94,0:55:32.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:32.94,0:55:33.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:33.94,0:55:34.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:34.94,0:55:36.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:36.19,0:55:37.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:37.19,0:55:38.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:38.19,0:55:39.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:39.19,0:55:40.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:40.19,0:55:41.19,Default,,0,0,0,,God bless you.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:41.19,0:56:00.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:00.53,0:56:09.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I would just like to ask for forgiveness, and I pray to surrender to the love of Jesus
Dialogue: 0,0:56:09.53,0:56:12.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Christ and to accept the gift of the resurrection.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:12.53,0:56:17.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know what you're saying.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:17.40,0:56:25.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I ask for forgiveness, and I pray to surrender to the love of Jesus Christ and to accept
Dialogue: 0,0:56:25.57,0:56:26.57,Default,,0,0,0,,the gift of the resurrection.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:26.57,0:56:27.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know what you're asking.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:27.57,0:56:29.86,Default,,0,0,0,,What is she talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:56:29.86,0:56:30.86,Default,,0,0,0,,She's just—
Dialogue: 0,0:56:30.86,0:56:31.86,Default,,0,0,0,,What about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:56:31.86,0:56:33.05,Default,,0,0,0,,What is the question?
Dialogue: 0,0:56:33.05,0:56:35.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I just pray—I ask for forgiveness.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:35.88,0:56:37.03,Default,,0,0,0,,She wants you to bless her.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:37.03,0:56:38.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:38.03,0:56:41.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I would like a blessing.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:41.21,0:56:42.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:42.21,0:56:43.21,Default,,0,0,0,,She's asking you for—
Dialogue: 0,0:56:43.21,0:56:44.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:44.21,0:56:45.21,Default,,0,0,0,,It's—the blessing is suitable.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:45.21,0:56:46.30,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:46.30,0:56:47.53,Default,,0,0,0,,So, I bless your search for the Lord Jesus Christ, your Savior.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:47.53,0:56:48.53,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll speak to you later.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:48.53,0:56:52.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:52.48,0:56:54.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:54.34,0:56:55.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:55.34,0:57:00.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:00.30,0:57:01.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:01.30,0:57:02.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:02.38,0:57:03.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:03.38,0:57:04.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:04.38,0:57:05.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:05.38,0:57:06.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:06.50,0:57:07.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:07.50,0:57:08.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:08.50,0:57:09.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:09.50,0:57:12.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:12.26,0:57:13.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:13.26,0:57:14.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:14.26,0:57:15.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Amen.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:15.42,0:57:16.42,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:16.42,0:57:17.42,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:17.42,0:57:18.42,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:18.42,0:57:22.96,Default,,0,0,0,,So, you need to learn how to speak before the Father for you in heaven.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:22.96,0:57:23.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:57:23.96,0:57:24.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:24.96,0:57:28.65,Default,,0,0,0,,.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:28.65,0:57:29.65,Default,,0,0,0,,He is a hard time—it is a feedback.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:29.65,0:57:30.65,Default,,0,0,0,,He is a hard time hearing.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:30.65,0:57:31.65,Default,,0,0,0,,If you're a Christian, then Jesus Christ
Dialogue: 0,0:57:31.65,0:57:33.46,Default,,0,0,0,,will be your advocate before the Father.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:33.46,0:57:36.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:36.28,0:57:37.55,Default,,0,0,0,,You want to work together.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:37.55,0:57:38.78,Default,,0,0,0,,You're an advocate before the Father.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:38.78,0:57:40.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:40.13,0:57:42.63,Default,,0,0,0,,He will speak for you before the Father.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:42.63,0:57:49.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to say I love you and I thank you for the work that you're doing.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:49.55,0:57:49.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:49.59,0:57:52.48,Default,,0,0,0,,and your presence in my life.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:52.69,0:57:53.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:53.51,0:57:54.82,Default,,0,0,0,,And I have a question
Dialogue: 0,0:57:54.82,0:57:56.90,Default,,0,0,0,,that I have a physical thing
Dialogue: 0,0:57:56.90,0:57:57.96,Default,,0,0,0,,that happens to me
Dialogue: 0,0:57:57.96,0:57:59.28,Default,,0,0,0,,that I can't explain
Dialogue: 0,0:57:59.28,0:58:02.67,Default,,0,0,0,,that I have a moment
Dialogue: 0,0:58:02.67,0:58:04.78,Default,,0,0,0,,of going faint
Dialogue: 0,0:58:04.78,0:58:07.21,Default,,0,0,0,,and then my heart starts racing.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:07.84,0:58:08.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:08.25,0:58:10.65,Default,,0,0,0,,And I don't eat sugar.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:11.17,0:58:11.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:11.40,0:58:13.21,Default,,0,0,0,,And I don't know,
Dialogue: 0,0:58:13.44,0:58:14.84,Default,,0,0,0,,and it's unrelated.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:15.25,0:58:16.53,Default,,0,0,0,,It's been going on for a few years.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:16.65,0:58:17.86,Default,,0,0,0,,It's atrial fibrillation.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:18.17,0:58:18.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Resist.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:18.38,0:58:20.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Atrial fibrillation.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:21.03,0:58:21.53,Default,,0,0,0,,You can cure it
Dialogue: 0,0:58:21.53,0:58:22.76,Default,,0,0,0,,with a half a tablet of,
Dialogue: 0,0:58:23.42,0:58:24.65,Default,,0,0,0,,what the hell is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:58:25.44,0:58:26.28,Default,,0,0,0,,No, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:27.40,0:58:27.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Atrial.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:28.46,0:58:28.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:58:29.26,0:58:29.73,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:30.30,0:58:30.48,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:30.94,0:58:31.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Atrial fib,
Dialogue: 0,0:58:32.65,0:58:33.82,Default,,0,0,0,,it'll come to me in a second.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:37.17,0:58:38.50,Default,,0,0,0,,It's easily curable,
Dialogue: 0,0:58:38.73,0:58:39.50,Default,,0,0,0,,cardiologists.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:40.21,0:58:40.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:41.05,0:58:42.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, when I went to
Dialogue: 0,0:58:43.09,0:58:44.67,Default,,0,0,0,,had an EKG and all that
Dialogue: 0,0:58:44.67,0:58:45.11,Default,,0,0,0,,and they said
Dialogue: 0,0:58:45.11,0:58:46.00,Default,,0,0,0,,there was no problem
Dialogue: 0,0:58:46.00,0:58:46.80,Default,,0,0,0,,with my heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:48.26,0:58:49.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, then you're not having
Dialogue: 0,0:58:49.23,0:58:51.15,Default,,0,0,0,,what you're saying
Dialogue: 0,0:58:51.15,0:58:51.59,Default,,0,0,0,,you're having.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:52.28,0:58:52.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:53.05,0:58:55.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I don't know what it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:55.13,0:58:56.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I just know that
Dialogue: 0,0:58:56.07,0:58:57.36,Default,,0,0,0,,unexpectedly,
Dialogue: 0,0:58:57.86,0:58:59.76,Default,,0,0,0,,my heart will just start racing
Dialogue: 0,0:58:59.76,0:59:01.38,Default,,0,0,0,,and then it will stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:01.38,0:59:02.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, they did a cardiogram
Dialogue: 0,0:59:02.53,0:59:04.25,Default,,0,0,0,,and said that it's not doing that.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:04.57,0:59:04.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:05.82,0:59:06.59,Default,,0,0,0,,So, I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:06.59,0:59:07.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Are they lying or what?
Dialogue: 0,0:59:08.03,0:59:08.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:08.86,0:59:09.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:10.34,0:59:10.71,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:10.75,0:59:11.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:11.17,0:59:11.71,Default,,0,0,0,,It's simple.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:12.26,0:59:13.30,Default,,0,0,0,,She has atrial fib.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:13.63,0:59:14.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:14.51,0:59:14.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:15.30,0:59:17.15,Default,,0,0,0,,You got paroxysmal
Dialogue: 0,0:59:17.15,0:59:18.61,Default,,0,0,0,,atrial fibrillation,
Dialogue: 0,0:59:19.11,0:59:21.44,Default,,0,0,0,,which is relatively benign.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:21.44,0:59:23.94,Default,,0,0,0,,However, your heart will stop
Dialogue: 0,0:59:23.94,0:59:26.92,Default,,0,0,0,,and then it may race
Dialogue: 0,0:59:26.92,0:59:27.78,Default,,0,0,0,,and then stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:28.17,0:59:29.71,Default,,0,0,0,,There's a simple medication
Dialogue: 0,0:59:29.71,0:59:31.21,Default,,0,0,0,,inexpensive generic
Dialogue: 0,0:59:31.21,0:59:33.19,Default,,0,0,0,,that stops it.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:33.69,0:59:35.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't think of the name
Dialogue: 0,0:59:35.09,0:59:35.86,Default,,0,0,0,,of it at the moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:36.07,0:59:36.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me see.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:46.48,0:59:46.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:47.21,0:59:47.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Beta blocker.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:48.65,0:59:48.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Yep.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:51.38,0:59:52.71,Default,,0,0,0,,It'll come to me later.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:57.36,0:59:58.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Any doctors who stop
Dialogue: 0,0:59:58.48,0:59:59.76,Default,,0,0,0,,what stops atrial fib?
Dialogue: 0,0:59:59.92,1:00:00.38,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a
Dialogue: 0,1:00:02.05,1:00:05.88,Default,,0,0,0,,well, I can't prescribe
Dialogue: 0,1:00:05.88,1:00:06.61,Default,,0,0,0,,for you under the present
Dialogue: 0,1:00:06.61,1:00:07.15,Default,,0,0,0,,circumstances.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:07.55,1:00:07.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:07.94,1:00:09.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway, it's obviously
Dialogue: 0,1:00:09.96,1:00:11.17,Default,,0,0,0,,atrial fibrillation.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:11.34,1:00:11.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:12.05,1:00:13.53,Default,,0,0,0,,That doctor that comes on
Dialogue: 0,1:00:13.53,1:00:15.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Fox News every Sunday morning
Dialogue: 0,1:00:15.46,1:00:16.36,Default,,0,0,0,,talked about it
Dialogue: 0,1:00:16.36,1:00:17.25,Default,,0,0,0,,about a month ago.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:17.42,1:00:18.63,Default,,0,0,0,,He devoted the whole program
Dialogue: 0,1:00:18.63,1:00:20.05,Default,,0,0,0,,to atrial fib.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:20.21,1:00:20.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:21.19,1:00:22.71,Default,,0,0,0,,You might write Fox News
Dialogue: 0,1:00:22.71,1:00:23.28,Default,,0,0,0,,and ask him,
Dialogue: 0,1:00:23.36,1:00:24.01,Default,,0,0,0,,who is that doctor
Dialogue: 0,1:00:24.01,1:00:25.32,Default,,0,0,0,,and get a copy of that CD.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:26.05,1:00:27.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I can research it.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:27.36,1:00:27.92,Default,,0,0,0,,What's his name?
Dialogue: 0,1:00:27.98,1:00:29.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Dr. Bloomberg or something?
Dialogue: 0,1:00:29.55,1:00:29.76,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:32.69,1:00:33.46,Default,,0,0,0,,He talked, anyway,
Dialogue: 0,1:00:33.51,1:00:34.69,Default,,0,0,0,,he talked about atrial fib
Dialogue: 0,1:00:34.69,1:00:36.28,Default,,0,0,0,,about a month ago.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:36.42,1:00:36.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:36.84,1:00:37.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:37.88,1:00:38.82,Default,,0,0,0,,In great detail.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:39.11,1:00:39.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:39.90,1:00:40.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:41.01,1:00:42.96,Default,,0,0,0,,And may I shake your hand?
Dialogue: 0,1:00:43.11,1:00:43.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:44.53,1:00:45.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, if I think of the name
Dialogue: 0,1:00:45.59,1:00:45.98,Default,,0,0,0,,of the med,
Dialogue: 0,1:00:46.01,1:00:47.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll just holler it out.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:47.71,1:00:48.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:49.05,1:00:49.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:50.73,1:00:52.09,Default,,0,0,0,,How can you not remember
Dialogue: 0,1:00:52.09,1:00:52.51,Default,,0,0,0,,that thing?
Dialogue: 0,1:00:53.05,1:00:56.90,Default,,0,0,0,,That's because we're
Dialogue: 0,1:00:56.90,1:00:57.96,Default,,0,0,0,,in a spiritual setting
Dialogue: 0,1:00:57.96,1:00:58.61,Default,,0,0,0,,and they ask you
Dialogue: 0,1:00:58.61,1:00:59.28,Default,,0,0,0,,medical questions.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:59.28,1:01:00.80,Default,,0,0,0,,They ask a linear question
Dialogue: 0,1:01:00.80,1:01:02.13,Default,,0,0,0,,in a non-linear dimension.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:03.36,1:01:04.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much
Dialogue: 0,1:01:04.40,1:01:05.09,Default,,0,0,0,,for today.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:05.15,1:01:06.09,Default,,0,0,0,,It's been a wonderful day,
Dialogue: 0,1:01:06.28,1:01:07.25,Default,,0,0,0,,wonderful experience.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:07.98,1:01:09.55,Default,,0,0,0,,And my question is,
Dialogue: 0,1:01:10.82,1:01:11.42,Default,,0,0,0,,can we,
Dialogue: 0,1:01:12.17,1:01:13.21,Default,,0,0,0,,do we sometimes,
Dialogue: 0,1:01:13.32,1:01:14.51,Default,,0,0,0,,come into this lifetime
Dialogue: 0,1:01:14.51,1:01:16.55,Default,,0,0,0,,with a karmically,
Dialogue: 0,1:01:16.78,1:01:17.96,Default,,0,0,0,,pre-karmically agreed,
Dialogue: 0,1:01:18.55,1:01:19.59,Default,,0,0,0,,what you might call
Dialogue: 0,1:01:19.59,1:01:20.57,Default,,0,0,0,,divine mission?
Dialogue: 0,1:01:21.09,1:01:21.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I think so.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:23.57,1:01:23.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Yep.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:24.26,1:01:25.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Would it be possible
Dialogue: 0,1:01:25.21,1:01:26.15,Default,,0,0,0,,if I held it in mind
Dialogue: 0,1:01:26.15,1:01:26.86,Default,,0,0,0,,to calibrate
Dialogue: 0,1:01:26.86,1:01:27.92,Default,,0,0,0,,what I think mine is,
Dialogue: 0,1:01:27.98,1:01:29.09,Default,,0,0,0,,what I'm pretty sure mine is?
Dialogue: 0,1:01:29.90,1:01:30.59,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you think
Dialogue: 0,1:01:30.59,1:01:31.44,Default,,0,0,0,,your divine mission is?
Dialogue: 0,1:01:32.92,1:01:34.05,Default,,0,0,0,,It's getting involved
Dialogue: 0,1:01:34.05,1:01:35.50,Default,,0,0,0,,with orphanage work
Dialogue: 0,1:01:35.50,1:01:36.42,Default,,0,0,0,,in Costa Rica.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:37.05,1:01:38.61,Default,,0,0,0,,And it's very, very diamond.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:40.65,1:01:41.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh-huh.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:41.36,1:01:41.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:43.51,1:01:45.15,Default,,0,0,0,,That would be a fulfillment
Dialogue: 0,1:01:45.15,1:01:45.67,Default,,0,0,0,,of his karmic mission.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:45.67,1:01:45.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:45.71,1:01:45.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:45.78,1:01:45.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:45.84,1:01:46.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:46.13,1:01:46.86,Default,,0,0,0,,It's like propensity
Dialogue: 0,1:01:46.86,1:01:49.30,Default,,0,0,0,,to help children.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:49.53,1:01:49.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:49.94,1:01:50.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:50.21,1:01:50.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:50.71,1:01:51.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:51.61,1:01:52.53,Default,,0,0,0,,That was all I wanted to know.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:52.69,1:01:53.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:53.51,1:01:54.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it okay to shake your hand, sir?
Dialogue: 0,1:01:54.78,1:01:55.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:56.55,1:01:56.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, God.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:57.05,1:01:57.80,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the name of the man?
Dialogue: 0,1:01:59.80,1:02:00.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Doctor,
Dialogue: 0,1:02:02.23,1:02:02.92,Default,,0,0,0,,to get his,
Dialogue: 0,1:02:07.26,1:02:07.71,Default,,0,0,0,,what is it?
Dialogue: 0,1:02:11.48,1:02:13.00,Default,,0,0,0,,He wrote a whole term
Dialogue: 0,1:02:13.57,1:02:15.07,Default,,0,0,0,,on how to do
Dialogue: 0,1:02:15.07,1:02:17.61,Default,,0,0,0,,clinics down in Costa Rica.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:17.90,1:02:18.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:18.65,1:02:19.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:19.19,1:02:19.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I wrote a paper,
Dialogue: 0,1:02:20.07,1:02:20.76,Default,,0,0,0,,low-cost
Dialogue: 0,1:02:20.76,1:02:23.13,Default,,0,0,0,,psychiatric
Dialogue: 0,1:02:23.13,1:02:25.13,Default,,0,0,0,,and addiction clinics.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:25.13,1:02:25.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Clinics.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:26.13,1:02:28.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Clinics for Central and South America,
Dialogue: 0,1:02:28.96,1:02:35.28,Default,,0,0,0,,which I wrote for some organization.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:35.28,1:02:36.78,Default,,0,0,0,,When he was knighted.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:36.78,1:02:38.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:38.59,1:02:38.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:38.78,1:02:40.13,Default,,0,0,0,,And he wrote that.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:40.13,1:02:41.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Low-cost clinics
Dialogue: 0,1:02:41.44,1:02:44.28,Default,,0,0,0,,for the disadvantaged
Dialogue: 0,1:02:44.28,1:02:46.09,Default,,0,0,0,,in Central and South America.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:46.09,1:02:49.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I wrote a paper on the subject, yes,
Dialogue: 0,1:02:49.17,1:02:50.88,Default,,0,0,0,,for which I received some honor.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:50.88,1:02:54.98,Default,,0,0,0,,When he was knighted into the state.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:54.98,1:02:58.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Order of, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:58.03,1:03:10.96,Default,,0,0,0,,The Order of St. John of Jerusalem.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:10.96,1:03:11.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:11.86,1:03:13.53,Default,,0,0,0,,The Order of St. John of the,
Dialogue: 0,1:03:13.53,1:03:19.05,Default,,0,0,0,,the Order of the Hospitalliers of St. John of Jerusalem,
Dialogue: 0,1:03:19.05,1:03:22.53,Default,,0,0,0,,which were one of the first crusades,
Dialogue: 0,1:03:22.53,1:03:25.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Christian crusades to the Holy Land, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:25.90,1:03:26.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:26.73,1:03:27.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:27.57,1:03:31.38,Default,,0,0,0,,And it was in that lifetime there
Dialogue: 0,1:03:31.38,1:03:34.94,Default,,0,0,0,,that we killed each other.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:34.94,1:03:36.55,Default,,0,0,0,,He killed me for Allah,
Dialogue: 0,1:03:36.55,1:03:38.13,Default,,0,0,0,,and I killed him for Jesus.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:40.67,1:03:42.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Had a lifetime there.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:42.51,1:03:43.36,Default,,0,0,0,,And I've met,
Dialogue: 0,1:03:43.36,1:03:44.36,Default,,0,0,0,,he's been,
Dialogue: 0,1:03:44.36,1:03:46.15,Default,,0,0,0,,a working partner of mine
Dialogue: 0,1:03:46.15,1:03:48.19,Default,,0,0,0,,throughout many centuries.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:48.19,1:03:49.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway,
Dialogue: 0,1:03:49.71,1:03:51.03,Default,,0,0,0,,it was during the crusades,
Dialogue: 0,1:03:51.03,1:03:54.28,Default,,0,0,0,,and I killed him for Jesus,
Dialogue: 0,1:03:54.28,1:03:56.67,Default,,0,0,0,,and he killed me for Allah.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:56.67,1:03:58.94,Default,,0,0,0,,We both went out of body at the same time,
Dialogue: 0,1:03:58.94,1:03:59.78,Default,,0,0,0,,looked at each other,
Dialogue: 0,1:03:59.78,1:04:02.78,Default,,0,0,0,,and split up laughing.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:02.78,1:04:04.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I said, this is too much.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:04.26,1:04:05.11,Default,,0,0,0,,He was out of,
Dialogue: 0,1:04:05.11,1:04:07.21,Default,,0,0,0,,both in our third bodies.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:07.21,1:04:08.65,Default,,0,0,0,,We both split laughing.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:08.65,1:04:09.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I killed him for Jesus,
Dialogue: 0,1:04:09.71,1:04:10.65,Default,,0,0,0,,he killed me for Allah.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:10.65,1:04:12.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Hysterical.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:12.67,1:04:15.01,Default,,0,0,0,,The world is still doing it.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:15.01,1:04:17.21,Default,,0,0,0,,But we saw that back in the year,
Dialogue: 0,1:04:17.78,1:04:20.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I forget, 12 something.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:20.61,1:04:21.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, go ahead.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:21.98,1:04:24.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I've enjoyed your sweet presence today.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:24.40,1:04:25.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:25.25,1:04:26.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:26.09,1:04:27.38,Default,,0,0,0,,And I just wanted to spend
Dialogue: 0,1:04:27.38,1:04:29.48,Default,,0,0,0,,a little bit more time closer,
Dialogue: 0,1:04:29.48,1:04:31.21,Default,,0,0,0,,and a handshake.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:31.21,1:04:32.11,Default,,0,0,0,,What'd she say?
Dialogue: 0,1:04:32.11,1:04:33.86,Default,,0,0,0,,She said, one.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:33.86,1:04:34.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, handshake.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:34.69,1:04:35.53,Default,,0,0,0,,And more presence.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:35.53,1:04:37.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:37.94,1:04:43.13,Default,,0,0,0,,You bet.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:43.13,1:04:43.98,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the name of that,
Dialogue: 0,1:04:43.98,1:04:45.32,Default,,0,0,0,,that I take every morning
Dialogue: 0,1:04:45.32,1:04:46.42,Default,,0,0,0,,when I cry this thing?
Dialogue: 0,1:04:48.63,1:04:49.80,Default,,0,0,0,,How could you take it every morning
Dialogue: 0,1:04:49.80,1:04:50.73,Default,,0,0,0,,and not remember it?
Dialogue: 0,1:04:50.73,1:04:52.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, it's unbelievable.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:52.17,1:04:53.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, go ahead.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:53.09,1:04:54.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I wanna thank you, Dr. Hawkins,
Dialogue: 0,1:04:54.86,1:04:56.17,Default,,0,0,0,,from the bottom of my heart.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:56.17,1:04:57.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:57.01,1:04:57.96,Default,,0,0,0,,And ask for your blessing.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:57.96,1:04:59.69,Default,,0,0,0,,And these two young men are here
Dialogue: 0,1:04:59.69,1:05:01.42,Default,,0,0,0,,from London to see you.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:01.42,1:05:02.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:02.25,1:05:04.38,Default,,0,0,0,,And they wanted also to shake your hand.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:04.38,1:05:05.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:05.40,1:05:06.34,Default,,0,0,0,,They're from London?
Dialogue: 0,1:05:06.34,1:05:07.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:07.19,1:05:09.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:09.23,1:05:11.38,Default,,0,0,0,,We're in London.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:11.38,1:05:13.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Central and East town.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:13.21,1:05:14.46,Default,,0,0,0,,From South London.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:14.46,1:05:15.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:15.30,1:05:16.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:16.23,1:05:18.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I just wanted to say that
Dialogue: 0,1:05:18.15,1:05:19.76,Default,,0,0,0,,it's not a big deal to us to come here,
Dialogue: 0,1:05:19.76,1:05:22.13,Default,,0,0,0,,and we're really thankful to be in your presence.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:22.13,1:05:22.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:22.98,1:05:23.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Love you very much.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:23.82,1:05:25.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for coming here.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:25.21,1:05:26.30,Default,,0,0,0,,We love London.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:26.82,1:05:30.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been there two or three times.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:30.25,1:05:34.96,Default,,0,0,0,,We both love London a lot.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:34.96,1:05:41.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, Doctor.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:41.42,1:05:44.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Where is it where they have Poet's Corner?
Dialogue: 0,1:05:44.26,1:05:45.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that what's on the other?
Dialogue: 0,1:05:45.11,1:05:46.00,Default,,0,0,0,,The Abbey.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:46.00,1:05:49.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Westminster Abbey, yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:49.01,1:05:55.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I always go to Westminster Abbey.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:55.05,1:05:58.17,Default,,0,0,0,,It's been under construction for over 1,000 years.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:58.17,1:06:05.11,Default,,0,0,0,,That's impressive.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:05.11,1:06:07.46,Default,,0,0,0,,They've been working on it for over 1,000 years
Dialogue: 0,1:06:07.46,1:06:12.38,Default,,0,0,0,,and haven't finished it yet.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:12.38,1:06:14.57,Default,,0,0,0,,That's dragging your feet.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:17.53,1:06:19.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Sister taught Coco.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:19.44,1:06:21.73,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the woman that taught Coco.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:21.73,1:06:22.73,Default,,0,0,0,,It could be her.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:22.73,1:06:24.73,Default,,0,0,0,,It was his sister who taught her.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:24.73,1:06:27.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:27.23,1:06:28.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:28.23,1:06:30.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Doctor, I bring you greetings from Eastern Canada.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:30.23,1:06:31.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:31.23,1:06:32.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I come from New Brunswick.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:32.23,1:06:33.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:33.23,1:06:35.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Which is even further east than Maine,
Dialogue: 0,1:06:35.23,1:06:36.23,Default,,0,0,0,,as you know.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:36.23,1:06:37.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:37.23,1:06:39.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I had a question,
Dialogue: 0,1:06:39.23,1:06:43.23,Default,,0,0,0,,and at about 12 minutes after 10 this morning,
Dialogue: 0,1:06:43.23,1:06:44.23,Default,,0,0,0,,it was answered.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:44.23,1:06:45.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:45.23,1:06:46.23,Default,,0,0,0,,That question, of course,
Dialogue: 0,1:06:46.23,1:06:49.65,Default,,0,0,0,,was whether I should be using compact fluorescent lights or not.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:49.65,1:06:50.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Whether I should be using what?
Dialogue: 0,1:06:51.65,1:06:53.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Compact fluorescent lights.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:53.65,1:06:56.65,Default,,0,0,0,,And then you answered that about 10 o'clock this morning.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:56.65,1:06:57.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:57.65,1:06:58.65,Default,,0,0,0,,So I've just enjoyed the day.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:58.65,1:06:59.65,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:59.65,1:07:01.65,Default,,0,0,0,,It is so very validating.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:01.65,1:07:02.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:02.65,1:07:07.88,Default,,0,0,0,,To read your books over and over and over.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:07.88,1:07:08.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:08.88,1:07:09.88,Default,,0,0,0,,To watch your DVDs.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:09.88,1:07:10.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:10.88,1:07:13.88,Default,,0,0,0,,And to have been here 28 months ago.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:13.88,1:07:14.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:14.88,1:07:15.88,Default,,0,0,0,,In December of 2006.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:15.88,1:07:16.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:16.88,1:07:19.88,Default,,0,0,0,,When you told us the story of the snake.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:19.88,1:07:20.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:20.88,1:07:23.88,Default,,0,0,0,,At that time, my oldest son and his wife was with us.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:23.88,1:07:25.88,Default,,0,0,0,,He, at the present time,
Dialogue: 0,1:07:25.88,1:07:28.88,Default,,0,0,0,,is suffering from a seven-millimeter kidney stone
Dialogue: 0,1:07:28.88,1:07:30.88,Default,,0,0,0,,and wasn't able to make the trip.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:30.88,1:07:31.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:31.88,1:07:36.09,Default,,0,0,0,,However, this child, my adult,
Dialogue: 0,1:07:36.09,1:07:39.13,Default,,0,0,0,,and my two parents would like to have a picture.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:40.13,1:07:42.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Could we do that?
Dialogue: 0,1:07:42.63,1:07:44.63,Default,,0,0,0,,They have a way of blasting those things now
Dialogue: 0,1:07:44.63,1:07:45.63,Default,,0,0,0,,and disintegrating them.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:45.63,1:07:46.63,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what he's waiting for.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:46.63,1:07:47.63,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:47.63,1:07:50.63,Default,,0,0,0,,The urologists are all on conference until Wednesday.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:50.63,1:07:51.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:51.63,1:07:52.63,Default,,0,0,0,,They disintegrate it now.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:52.63,1:07:53.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:53.63,1:07:54.63,Default,,0,0,0,,So we would like a picture with the family if I could.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:54.63,1:07:55.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:55.63,1:07:56.63,Default,,0,0,0,,They disintegrate it now.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:56.63,1:07:57.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:57.76,1:07:58.76,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,1:07:58.76,1:07:59.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you talk or something?
Dialogue: 0,1:07:59.76,1:08:03.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Digoxin.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:03.94,1:08:04.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Digoxin.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:04.94,1:08:06.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Digoxin.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:06.26,1:08:07.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:07.26,1:08:11.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Digoxin.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:11.75,1:08:12.75,Default,,0,0,0,,That's for, like, heart problems.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:12.75,1:08:13.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Who gets this?
Dialogue: 0,1:08:13.75,1:08:14.75,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:14.75,1:08:15.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:15.75,1:08:17.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you do one more, please?
Dialogue: 0,1:08:17.80,1:08:30.10,Default,,0,0,0,,This is for the older boy.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:30.10,1:08:31.10,Default,,0,0,0,,That is so painful to have kidney stones.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:31.10,1:08:35.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I feel so sorry for him.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:35.10,1:08:37.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:37.26,1:08:45.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me see.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:45.59,1:08:46.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me see.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:46.59,1:08:47.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me see.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:47.59,1:08:48.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me see.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:48.59,1:08:49.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me see.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:49.59,1:08:50.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me see.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:50.59,1:08:51.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:51.59,1:08:52.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Love you.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:52.59,1:08:53.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:53.59,1:08:54.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:54.59,1:09:00.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, indeed.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:00.64,1:09:01.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:01.64,1:09:05.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:05.77,1:09:06.77,Default,,0,0,0,,She went to Al-Anon and took step one.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:06.77,1:09:07.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:07.77,1:09:12.10,Default,,0,0,0,,For that lady that had the heart circulation, is that the drug?
Dialogue: 0,1:09:12.10,1:09:13.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, hell no.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:13.10,1:09:14.10,Default,,0,0,0,,It's better than the one.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:14.10,1:09:15.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know who it is.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:15.19,1:09:18.76,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:18.76,1:09:19.76,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not the one.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:19.76,1:09:20.76,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:20.76,1:09:21.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:21.76,1:09:22.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:22.76,1:09:23.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Dr. Hopkins.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:23.96,1:09:24.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much for your teachings.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:24.96,1:09:31.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm a physician, and I'm trying to incorporate many of your teachings in working with my
Dialogue: 0,1:09:31.96,1:09:32.96,Default,,0,0,0,,patients.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:32.96,1:09:33.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:33.96,1:09:39.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I've used different healing practices or sent them to different types of healers.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:39.42,1:09:45.30,Default,,0,0,0,,In Truth Versus Falsehood, you calibrated different healing practices, whether it be
Dialogue: 0,1:09:45.30,1:09:52.52,Default,,0,0,0,,homeopathy, acupuncture, Reiki.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:52.52,1:09:58.26,Default,,0,0,0,,You said energy medicine calibrated quite high, and I was trying to discern what energy
Dialogue: 0,1:09:58.26,1:10:01.96,Default,,0,0,0,,medicine is compared to acupuncture or Reiki.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:01.96,1:10:03.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, acupuncture is a form of energy medicine.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:03.96,1:10:04.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:04.96,1:10:07.46,Default,,0,0,0,,So I didn't understand what the difference was.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:07.46,1:10:14.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, energy medicine is just a general classification, kinesiology, acupuncture, things that are not
Dialogue: 0,1:10:14.89,1:10:21.06,Default,,0,0,0,,within the tight scientific discipline of traditional medicine.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:21.06,1:10:25.18,Default,,0,0,0,,So it's a general classification that you're giving it.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:25.18,1:10:26.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:26.18,1:10:27.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:27.53,1:10:28.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:28.53,1:10:29.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:29.53,1:10:30.53,Default,,0,0,0,,If I may have a blessing and a picture?
Dialogue: 0,1:10:30.53,1:10:31.53,Default,,0,0,0,,You can have a blessing, indeed.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:31.53,1:10:32.53,Default,,0,0,0,,God bless you.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:32.53,1:10:34.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:34.14,1:10:37.60,Default,,0,0,0,,God bless you.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:37.60,1:10:38.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Amen.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:38.60,1:10:40.14,Default,,0,0,0,,God bless you.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:40.14,1:10:41.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Amen.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:41.14,1:10:48.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, the person that asked me about that cardiac med for atrial fibrillation will pester me
Dialogue: 0,1:10:48.63,1:10:51.31,Default,,0,0,0,,until I answer it.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:51.31,1:10:55.92,Default,,0,0,0,,If you call the office, the office will tell you.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:55.92,1:10:56.92,Default,,0,0,0,,What day is today?
Dialogue: 0,1:10:56.92,1:10:57.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Saturday.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:57.92,1:10:58.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Saturday, all right.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:58.92,1:11:00.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Monday.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:00.34,1:11:05.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Today's Monday?
Dialogue: 0,1:11:05.94,1:11:06.94,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:06.94,1:11:11.51,Default,,0,0,0,,If you call the office on Monday and ask, what is the med to take for atrial fibrillation,
Dialogue: 0,1:11:11.51,1:11:13.31,Default,,0,0,0,,the girl will tell you.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:13.31,1:11:18.06,Default,,0,0,0,,When I'm in the nonlinear, it's very hard to jump back into the nonlinear.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:18.06,1:11:20.06,Default,,0,0,0,,You have to jump back into the linear and think of something definitively.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:20.06,1:11:21.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:21.06,1:11:23.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:23.15,1:11:26.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I just wanted to say hello and have a moment.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:26.27,1:11:27.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:27.27,1:11:28.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:28.27,1:11:29.51,Default,,0,0,0,,METOPROLOL.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:29.51,1:11:30.51,Default,,0,0,0,,That's it.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:30.51,1:11:31.51,Default,,0,0,0,,METOPROLOL.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:31.51,1:11:32.89,Default,,0,0,0,,METO, M-E-T-O-P-R-O-L-O-L.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:32.89,1:11:35.30,Default,,0,0,0,,It's for rhythmic disorders.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:35.30,1:11:36.30,Default,,0,0,0,,It's cheap, and it's generic.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:36.30,1:11:37.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:37.30,1:11:39.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:39.19,1:11:40.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:40.19,1:11:41.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:41.26,1:11:42.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:42.26,1:11:43.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:43.26,1:11:44.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:44.26,1:11:46.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:46.11,1:11:47.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:47.11,1:11:48.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:48.11,1:11:49.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:49.43,1:11:50.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:50.43,1:11:57.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:57.59,1:11:58.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:58.59,1:12:00.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:00.15,1:12:01.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:01.15,1:12:09.34,Default,,0,0,0,,METOPROLOL is generic, and half a tablet of METOPROLOL a day stops atrial fib.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:09.34,1:12:10.39,Default,,0,0,0,,It came out of nowhere.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:10.39,1:12:13.30,Default,,0,0,0,,That's was not the result of a .
Dialogue: 0,1:12:13.30,1:12:14.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I asked the field.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:14.80,1:12:15.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello, doc.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:15.89,1:12:16.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello, Susan.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:16.89,1:12:19.26,Default,,0,0,0,,It's lovely to be back again from Australia.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:19.26,1:12:20.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, my goodness.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:21.93,1:12:24.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Just a little something to say, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:25.06,1:12:29.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm just kinkすごい.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:29.40,1:12:30.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Australia?
Dialogue: 0,1:12:31.40,1:12:32.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:32.40,1:12:33.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Open the way.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:33.40,1:12:34.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't think I can.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:34.35,1:12:42.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd like to ask for blessings again for Down Under and the family and I suppose myself as well, if that's possible.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:43.89,1:12:45.64,Default,,0,0,0,,It's great to be back again.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:47.06,1:12:48.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, God bless you.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:48.09,1:12:54.88,Default,,0,0,0,,And I see my blessing worked because Australia did not drop off the planet.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:56.92,1:12:58.64,Default,,0,0,0,,This is where Australia is down here.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:58.72,1:13:02.03,Default,,0,0,0,,It should fall down via gravity, but it stays there.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:02.34,1:13:03.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:03.23,1:13:03.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:03.64,1:13:05.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought you'd appreciate it.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:05.27,1:13:05.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Your blessings worked.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:05.53,1:13:06.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:06.47,1:13:06.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:08.27,1:13:12.52,Default,,0,0,0,,And I was wondering, I had my mother's jewelry made up into a pendant to wear.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:13.02,1:13:15.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I was wondering if you would bless that for me, please.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:16.15,1:13:17.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold it and bless it.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:17.53,1:13:18.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, dear.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:18.27,1:13:21.61,Default,,0,0,0,,What a lovely, lovely thing to have the blessing of.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:21.68,1:13:22.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:22.18,1:13:22.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:22.57,1:13:23.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:23.52,1:13:24.88,Default,,0,0,0,,And I'd just like to shake hands.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:25.14,1:13:25.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:25.52,1:13:29.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, Doc, very much for all your help in my life.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:29.73,1:13:29.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:29.76,1:13:30.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh-huh.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:30.11,1:13:31.31,Default,,0,0,0,,And all of us.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:31.53,1:13:32.22,Default,,0,0,0,,We're so grateful.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:32.34,1:13:33.61,Default,,0,0,0,,We're so grateful for your tape.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:33.64,1:13:34.03,Default,,0,0,0,,It's done.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:34.03,1:13:34.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Where abouts are you in Australia?
Dialogue: 0,1:13:35.27,1:13:36.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Near Byron Bay.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:36.71,1:13:37.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Byron Bay.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:37.09,1:13:41.85,Default,,0,0,0,,And also, I have family in Sydney, so I go backwards and forwards a bit.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:42.22,1:13:42.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:42.43,1:13:45.18,Default,,0,0,0,,And Byron Bay's got that high vortex of energy like here.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:45.68,1:13:48.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Dermot, behind you, he used to live in Australia.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:48.55,1:13:49.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, really?
Dialogue: 0,1:13:49.43,1:13:49.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:50.01,1:13:50.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:51.10,1:13:51.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:51.81,1:13:52.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, well, there's a couple of us.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:53.06,1:13:55.22,Default,,0,0,0,,The next lady is as well from Australia.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:55.81,1:13:59.17,Default,,0,0,0,,So we're very, very grateful for all you've done for us.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:59.77,1:14:00.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh-huh.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:00.09,1:14:00.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:00.48,1:14:01.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:01.39,1:14:01.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:01.75,1:14:01.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:02.55,1:14:02.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:02.81,1:14:03.67,Default,,0,0,0,,We have a lot of course.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:03.71,1:14:05.02,Default,,0,0,0,,We have a lot of correspondence in Australia.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:05.51,1:14:05.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:06.40,1:14:06.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:07.06,1:14:09.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Someday, I hope.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:09.36,1:14:09.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:10.02,1:14:12.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, we'd love you to come, but...
Dialogue: 0,1:14:12.88,1:14:14.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Actually, it's not that long, the flight.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:14.46,1:14:14.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, no.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:15.06,1:14:17.26,Default,,0,0,0,,It's only a couple of days on the plane and in the airport.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:18.02,1:14:22.69,Default,,0,0,0,,A couple of days in the airport floors and...
Dialogue: 0,1:14:22.69,1:14:23.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:23.43,1:14:23.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:23.84,1:14:24.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:25.42,1:14:25.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Well.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:26.50,1:14:26.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Well.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:27.57,1:14:29.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe next time.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:29.61,1:14:34.42,Default,,0,0,0,,You see, they got these supersonic airliners, and when they get them perfected,
Dialogue: 0,1:14:34.65,1:14:35.80,Default,,0,0,0,,you know, you bounce off.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:35.81,1:14:42.35,Default,,0,0,0,,They bounce off the atmosphere, and I'm going to try and get some big country like China
Dialogue: 0,1:14:42.35,1:14:51.25,Default,,0,0,0,,interested in producing them so it's profit-making, but it will only take, you know, maybe two
Dialogue: 0,1:14:51.25,1:14:52.36,Default,,0,0,0,,hours to get to Australia.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:52.94,1:14:54.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, that'd be amazing.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:54.78,1:14:56.77,Default,,0,0,0,,So a bit like a hovercraft on the sea.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:56.77,1:14:57.36,Default,,0,0,0,,No, no.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:57.40,1:15:03.52,Default,,0,0,0,,They're supersonic, and they go beyond the atmosphere, and then they come down, and the
Dialogue: 0,1:15:03.52,1:15:06.22,Default,,0,0,0,,resistance of the atmosphere, they bounce off the atmosphere again.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:06.22,1:15:08.44,Default,,0,0,0,,And then that gives them a bounce like a kangaroo.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:08.90,1:15:09.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:09.94,1:15:10.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:12.05,1:15:16.64,Default,,0,0,0,,So you can bounce from here to Australia in a matter of a couple hours.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:17.68,1:15:20.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure some big country will take it on.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:21.18,1:15:26.64,Default,,0,0,0,,And you've looked at all the procedure for this, the invention, and...
Dialogue: 0,1:15:26.64,1:15:28.81,Default,,0,0,0,,It's already a perfected thing.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:28.94,1:15:34.31,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just, you know, make it commercially worthwhile to pursue.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:34.72,1:15:35.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:35.09,1:15:37.06,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, you need a couple billion dollars.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:37.09,1:15:39.09,Default,,0,0,0,,You need a couple billion dollars to invest.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:39.09,1:15:40.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:40.09,1:15:42.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm figuring the Chinese or somebody will run in there and grab it, because it's a very
Dialogue: 0,1:15:42.59,1:15:43.59,Default,,0,0,0,,open...
Dialogue: 0,1:15:43.59,1:15:47.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Think of all the people that, you know, haven't got three or four days to get someplace.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:47.47,1:15:48.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, exactly.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:48.47,1:15:49.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:49.47,1:15:50.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:50.47,1:15:51.47,Default,,0,0,0,,You get from New York to London in, you know, a half hour.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:51.47,1:15:52.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, fantastic.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:52.47,1:15:57.76,Default,,0,0,0,,And from London to India in maybe two or three hours.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:57.76,1:16:03.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Another hour or two, and you're over in Australia, so you can circumvent the globe in a matter
Dialogue: 0,1:16:03.06,1:16:04.06,Default,,0,0,0,,of hours.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:04.06,1:16:05.06,Default,,0,0,0,,It's amazing.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:05.06,1:16:06.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I think that it is...
Dialogue: 0,1:16:06.06,1:16:07.10,Default,,0,0,0,,That's so profitable, potentially.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:07.10,1:16:09.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Somebody with big bucks will go into it.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:09.69,1:16:13.60,Default,,0,0,0,,And there they were going around the world in 80 days.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:13.60,1:16:14.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:14.60,1:16:15.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:15.60,1:16:16.60,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:16.60,1:16:17.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, Doc.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:17.60,1:16:18.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:18.60,1:16:19.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Could I take a...
Dialogue: 0,1:16:19.60,1:16:20.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I have a photo.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:20.60,1:16:21.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:21.60,1:16:22.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Very quickly.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:22.85,1:16:23.85,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:23.85,1:16:24.85,Default,,0,0,0,,We have 10 minutes left, you know.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:24.85,1:16:25.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:25.85,1:16:26.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Your time is my time.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:26.85,1:16:27.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:27.85,1:16:28.85,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll move along faster.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:28.85,1:16:29.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Run.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:29.85,1:16:30.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Run, rabbit.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:30.85,1:16:32.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Run.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:32.50,1:16:33.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:33.50,1:16:34.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Run, rabbit.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:34.88,1:16:35.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Run.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:35.88,1:16:36.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, sweetheart.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:36.88,1:16:37.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:37.88,1:16:38.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:38.88,1:16:40.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:40.89,1:16:41.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Also from Australia.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:41.89,1:16:42.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I think that'll work, that one.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:42.89,1:16:43.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:43.89,1:16:44.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, great.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:44.89,1:16:46.00,Default,,0,0,0,,And if possible, that one.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:46.00,1:16:47.00,Default,,0,0,0,,And...
Dialogue: 0,1:16:47.00,1:16:48.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:48.00,1:16:49.00,Default,,0,0,0,,And what would you like?
Dialogue: 0,1:16:49.00,1:16:50.00,Default,,0,0,0,,If you have any advice, please, for heavy metal toxicity?
Dialogue: 0,1:16:50.00,1:16:51.51,Default,,0,0,0,,They usually chelate them out.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:51.51,1:16:52.51,Default,,0,0,0,,What heavy metal are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,1:16:52.51,1:16:53.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Mercury and lead, mainly.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:53.51,1:16:54.51,Default,,0,0,0,,And if you...
Dialogue: 0,1:16:54.51,1:16:55.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, heavy metals are usually chelated out with very high doses of ascorbic acid.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:55.51,1:16:59.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:59.46,1:17:00.46,Default,,0,0,0,,The equivalent of...
Dialogue: 0,1:17:00.46,1:17:01.46,Default,,0,0,0,,The equivalent of...
Dialogue: 0,1:17:01.46,1:17:02.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:02.46,1:17:03.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:03.46,1:17:04.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:04.46,1:17:05.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:05.46,1:17:06.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:06.46,1:17:07.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:07.46,1:17:08.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:08.46,1:17:09.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:09.46,1:17:10.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:10.46,1:17:11.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:11.46,1:17:14.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:14.40,1:17:15.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:15.40,1:17:16.40,Default,,0,0,0,,The chelate, C-H-E-L-A-T-E.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:16.40,1:17:17.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:17.40,1:17:20.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Chelated out with high doses of ascorbic acid.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:20.43,1:17:21.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:21.43,1:17:28.42,Default,,0,0,0,,The only cases I had in my years in clinical work, I chelated them out.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:28.42,1:17:34.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I think I told you I had one guy who was as mad as a hatter.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:34.69,1:17:43.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway, he was a patient who was dragged around to see 50 doctors, all the chiefs of psychiatry
Dialogue: 0,1:17:43.06,1:17:47.18,Default,,0,0,0,,here and there and there, and he was hopeless, so he specialized in hopeless cases.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:47.18,1:17:48.23,Default,,0,0,0,,So they bring this guy in.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:48.23,1:17:49.39,Default,,0,0,0,,So they bring this guy in.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:49.43,1:17:52.56,Default,,0,0,0,,He's been everywhere, and he's crazy as a loon.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:53.30,1:17:55.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, nuts, nuts, nuts.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:56.85,1:17:59.88,Default,,0,0,0,,My mind said, he's as mad as a hatter.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:00.68,1:18:02.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I said, oh, he's got mercury poisoning.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:03.98,1:18:04.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:04.93,1:18:08.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Turned out the previous summer he'd been out spraying stuff in some orchard,
Dialogue: 0,1:18:09.48,1:18:11.68,Default,,0,0,0,,a mercury-containing orchard spray,
Dialogue: 0,1:18:12.52,1:18:14.31,Default,,0,0,0,,and he was as mad as a hatter.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:15.06,1:18:19.57,Default,,0,0,0,,So we chelated the mercury out with high doses of ascorbic acid,
Dialogue: 0,1:18:19.85,1:18:23.31,Default,,0,0,0,,including intravenous, and he recovered completely.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:24.84,1:18:25.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:26.71,1:18:29.67,Default,,0,0,0,,And I'll get you to sign that you're coming to Australia
Dialogue: 0,1:18:29.67,1:18:31.28,Default,,0,0,0,,as soon as that plane's invented.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:31.28,1:18:35.17,Default,,0,0,0,,As soon as they get that bouncer off the atmosphere.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:35.44,1:18:36.82,Default,,0,0,0,,It bounces on the atmosphere.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:40.71,1:18:47.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:47.82,1:18:50.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I wanted to say thank you to both of you.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:50.14,1:18:51.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I really had a lot of fun today,
Dialogue: 0,1:18:51.75,1:18:55.10,Default,,0,0,0,,and I wanted to ask for a blessing for me and for my home.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:55.78,1:18:57.98,Default,,0,0,0,,God bless you and your home, lovely lady.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:57.98,1:19:01.26,Default,,0,0,0,,And a picture.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:11.60,1:19:12.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:12.39,1:19:19.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:19.67,1:19:21.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I have a question.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:23.64,1:19:29.78,Default,,0,0,0,,At what consciousness level are you at when you have self-realization,
Dialogue: 0,1:19:30.05,1:19:31.63,Default,,0,0,0,,when you realize that you're a soul?
Dialogue: 0,1:19:32.56,1:19:33.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that 500?
Dialogue: 0,1:19:40.94,1:19:43.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Saintliness is around 570.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:44.47,1:19:46.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Enlightenment begins at 600.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:47.89,1:19:50.71,Default,,0,0,0,,And then there are various levels of enlightenment.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:53.93,1:19:54.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay?
Dialogue: 0,1:19:54.15,1:19:54.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:55.31,1:19:56.72,Default,,0,0,0,,And salvation, as mentioned,
Dialogue: 0,1:19:56.72,1:19:59.93,Default,,0,0,0,,in the Course in Miracles, what level would that be?
Dialogue: 0,1:19:59.93,1:20:03.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Salvation is not a level of consciousness.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:03.26,1:20:03.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:03.61,1:20:04.31,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:04.31,1:20:06.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Can I take your picture?
Dialogue: 0,1:20:06.21,1:20:06.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:06.78,1:20:07.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:07.05,1:20:14.03,Default,,0,0,0,,The workbook in Course in Miracles is at 600.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:15.06,1:20:16.72,Default,,0,0,0,,The textbook is at 550.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:21.82,1:20:22.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:22.18,1:20:26.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello, Dr. Huggins.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:27.31,1:20:27.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello, Susan.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:27.80,1:20:29.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:31.26,1:20:38.93,Default,,0,0,0,,In our devotion and duality group in Sedona, we use a prayer.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:38.93,1:20:39.14,Default,,0,0,0,,We pray.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:39.14,1:20:39.43,Default,,0,0,0,,We pray.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:39.43,1:20:39.68,Default,,0,0,0,,We pray.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:39.68,1:20:39.77,Default,,0,0,0,,We pray.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:39.77,1:20:39.81,Default,,0,0,0,,We pray.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:39.81,1:20:39.88,Default,,0,0,0,,We pray.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:39.88,1:20:39.97,Default,,0,0,0,,We pray.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:39.97,1:20:40.23,Default,,0,0,0,,We pray.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:40.23,1:20:40.27,Default,,0,0,0,,We pray.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:40.27,1:20:40.34,Default,,0,0,0,,We pray.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:40.34,1:20:40.93,Default,,0,0,0,,We pray.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:40.93,1:20:41.00,Default,,0,0,0,,We pray.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:41.00,1:20:41.07,Default,,0,0,0,,We pray.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:41.07,1:20:41.10,Default,,0,0,0,,We pray.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:41.10,1:20:41.14,Default,,0,0,0,,We pray.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:41.14,1:20:41.18,Default,,0,0,0,,We pray.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:41.18,1:20:47.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I am a servant of you, my Lord, and I ask for your divine will to be revealed to me.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:48.31,1:20:51.44,Default,,0,0,0,,And the question is, how in the midst of...
Dialogue: 0,1:20:51.44,1:20:52.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not understanding.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:52.51,1:20:52.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I am.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:53.13,1:20:53.51,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:55.42,1:20:55.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Go ahead.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:55.81,1:21:02.14,Default,,0,0,0,,In the midst of imagination and some thoughts, to learn to recognize the voice of the God.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:07.47,1:21:08.85,Default,,0,0,0,,To recognize the God.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:08.85,1:21:12.65,Default,,0,0,0,,How we can, yes, learn to recognize the voice of the higher.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:12.93,1:21:18.98,Default,,0,0,0,,How do you recognize the voice of God?
Dialogue: 0,1:21:18.98,1:21:21.14,Default,,0,0,0,,When...
Dialogue: 0,1:21:21.14,1:21:23.78,Default,,0,0,0,,If you question it, it's not the voice of God,
Dialogue: 0,1:21:23.86,1:21:26.25,Default,,0,0,0,,because the voice of God is self-revealing
Dialogue: 0,1:21:26.25,1:21:27.60,Default,,0,0,0,,that it is the voice of God.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:28.56,1:21:30.15,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a prayer. It's a prayer for God,
Dialogue: 0,1:21:30.26,1:21:34.65,Default,,0,0,0,,especially in moments when you're in a difficult decision
Dialogue: 0,1:21:34.65,1:21:36.53,Default,,0,0,0,,and then you ask the divine,
Dialogue: 0,1:21:36.73,1:21:40.18,Default,,0,0,0,,what would be the good for me, for my evolution?
Dialogue: 0,1:21:40.68,1:21:40.88,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,1:21:41.07,1:21:44.17,Default,,0,0,0,,In moments of questioning,
Dialogue: 0,1:21:44.52,1:21:47.28,Default,,0,0,0,,which direction to turn,
Dialogue: 0,1:21:47.28,1:21:54.18,Default,,0,0,0,,you ask for, with this prayer, you ask for guidance.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:54.43,1:21:54.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:54.60,1:21:58.32,Default,,0,0,0,,So how do you know that it's answering you?
Dialogue: 0,1:21:58.48,1:22:00.05,Default,,0,0,0,,It comes as a knowingness.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:01.65,1:22:04.38,Default,,0,0,0,,If there's any question, then that's not the answer.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:06.06,1:22:09.15,Default,,0,0,0,,The voice for God is accompanied by certainty.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:11.19,1:22:11.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Certainty.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:13.06,1:22:13.89,Default,,0,0,0,,If there's still a question,
Dialogue: 0,1:22:14.02,1:22:15.42,Default,,0,0,0,,it's because your mind is playing with it.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:16.92,1:22:20.93,Default,,0,0,0,,So if all of a sudden you get an answer to a dilemma
Dialogue: 0,1:22:20.93,1:22:21.84,Default,,0,0,0,,that you've been...
Dialogue: 0,1:22:21.85,1:22:24.42,Default,,0,0,0,,and you get this answer...
Dialogue: 0,1:22:24.42,1:22:25.52,Default,,0,0,0,,It comes as a clarification.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:25.89,1:22:27.10,Default,,0,0,0,,It comes as a clarification.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:27.34,1:22:27.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:27.64,1:22:29.42,Default,,0,0,0,,All of a sudden, you know...
Dialogue: 0,1:22:29.42,1:22:30.42,Default,,0,0,0,,It's simple and obvious.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:30.43,1:22:31.18,Default,,0,0,0,,It's simple and obvious.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:33.68,1:22:34.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:35.02,1:22:36.03,Default,,0,0,0,,May I ask you a blessing?
Dialogue: 0,1:22:37.85,1:22:38.72,Default,,0,0,0,,God bless you.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:38.73,1:22:40.68,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the man from Russia, honey, that came here.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:40.80,1:22:41.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:42.92,1:22:43.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, wonderful.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:44.11,1:22:44.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:44.35,1:22:45.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:46.38,1:22:53.78,Default,,0,0,0,,My question maybe is similar to his.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:54.72,1:22:57.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I have been questioning that I was...
Dialogue: 0,1:22:57.90,1:23:00.06,Default,,0,0,0,,focused too much on others' needs.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:00.81,1:23:04.21,Default,,0,0,0,,And I've been trying to get clear on my needs and meet them.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:04.81,1:23:09.90,Default,,0,0,0,,But then I start questioning if that's laziness and self-centeredness.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:10.44,1:23:14.14,Default,,0,0,0,,How can there be a conflict between the needs of others and your own?
Dialogue: 0,1:23:14.44,1:23:15.67,Default,,0,0,0,,It's how you're defining it.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:16.21,1:23:17.28,Default,,0,0,0,,There is no difference.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:19.06,1:23:24.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Taking care of children and their needs is taking care of myself.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:25.02,1:23:25.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,1:23:26.34,1:23:29.38,Default,,0,0,0,,My need to be the father, the mother, the parent, the helper.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:30.10,1:23:32.19,Default,,0,0,0,,To fulfill my potentiality.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:32.89,1:23:34.00,Default,,0,0,0,,So you can't differentiate.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:34.56,1:23:36.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm doing this for this person and not myself.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:37.23,1:23:39.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Or I'm just doing it for myself and not this person.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:40.15,1:23:41.35,Default,,0,0,0,,They're both the same.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:43.60,1:23:44.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:44.68,1:23:48.06,Default,,0,0,0,,What you sacrifice for others, you're also sacrificing for yourself.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:48.88,1:23:51.81,Default,,0,0,0,,And what you sacrifice for yourself, you're also sacrificing for others.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:51.81,1:23:55.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Because the less egoistic you are, the more you can serve others.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:56.89,1:24:01.02,Default,,0,0,0,,So you're just artificially dividing it as though they're two different things.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:01.02,1:24:02.05,Default,,0,0,0,,They're not two different things.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:03.03,1:24:08.68,Default,,0,0,0,,And then maybe just let daily tasks go to the side if they need to, to be more.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:09.27,1:24:09.84,Default,,0,0,0,,And then what?
Dialogue: 0,1:24:10.23,1:24:15.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Let daily tasks go to the side, you know, in order to be more what?
Dialogue: 0,1:24:15.35,1:24:17.02,Default,,0,0,0,,In service to the other or?
Dialogue: 0,1:24:17.68,1:24:18.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, sometimes things happen.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:18.98,1:24:21.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Daily tasks are service to the other, aren't they?
Dialogue: 0,1:24:22.47,1:24:25.93,Default,,0,0,0,,You're creating an artificial this or that versus that.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:26.28,1:24:27.43,Default,,0,0,0,,They're all the same.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:29.46,1:24:32.00,Default,,0,0,0,,You're giving service to life, to life.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:33.84,1:24:38.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Dusting the house, feeding the chickens, making the children dinner,
Dialogue: 0,1:24:38.72,1:24:39.97,Default,,0,0,0,,taking care of your aged mother.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:40.19,1:24:41.07,Default,,0,0,0,,It's all the same.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:41.35,1:24:44.06,Default,,0,0,0,,It's all service to life in all of life's expressions.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:44.96,1:24:45.93,Default,,0,0,0,,They're not different things.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:46.03,1:24:48.61,Default,,0,0,0,,They're all the same thing, but it's applied to different things.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:50.01,1:24:51.43,Default,,0,0,0,,That's helpful, service to life.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:51.56,1:24:52.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:52.32,1:24:52.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:52.60,1:24:52.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:52.85,1:24:53.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:53.47,1:24:53.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:56.68,1:24:57.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:02.18,1:25:02.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:05.63,1:25:07.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for all of the work that you've done.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:09.60,1:25:11.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm very grateful to be here.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:14.81,1:25:22.69,Default,,0,0,0,,When I am studying your work, I find it difficult to apply to myself in a very loving way.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:24.39,1:25:36.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder how to truly forgive myself, how to accept my humanness as I am trying to progress.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:37.57,1:25:39.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, you could do it piecemeal.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:39.92,1:25:43.06,Default,,0,0,0,,In you is the child, the adult, and the parent.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:43.98,1:25:46.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Start maybe forgiving the child.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:47.21,1:25:48.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Then move on to the parent.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:48.44,1:25:52.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, to the adult, then move on to the parent.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:54.00,1:25:55.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I would work the other way.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:56.34,1:25:59.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I would work with the child, and then the parent, and then the adult.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:04.75,1:26:05.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:06.09,1:26:06.82,Default,,0,0,0,,May I have a blessing?
Dialogue: 0,1:26:07.25,1:26:07.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:11.23,1:26:13.50,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, identify the child within you.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:13.73,1:26:14.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Forgive and love the child.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:16.53,1:26:20.22,Default,,0,0,0,,And then the child always leads right to the adult, the parent.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:21.46,1:26:24.97,Default,,0,0,0,,And then you heal the parent, and then that leads to the adult.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:25.11,1:26:28.10,Default,,0,0,0,,By that time, the adult's relatively easy to heal.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:32.78,1:26:34.09,Default,,0,0,0,,It's different in each person.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:45.68,1:26:46.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi, Dr. Hawkins.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:46.47,1:26:46.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:47.31,1:26:48.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi, Susan.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:49.27,1:26:53.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm using the calibration technique in my work.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:53.39,1:26:55.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm a doctor, so I calibrate lectures.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:56.00,1:27:03.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I calibrate journals and medical articles, really to find out, should I read this?
Dialogue: 0,1:27:03.57,1:27:07.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Many times I find I don't need to read a lot of the medical articles.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:07.69,1:27:08.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Many times she finds out what?
Dialogue: 0,1:27:08.93,1:27:12.27,Default,,0,0,0,,She doesn't need to read the medical articles.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:12.35,1:27:12.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, oh.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:12.82,1:27:13.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:13.31,1:27:13.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:13.47,1:27:13.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh-huh.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:13.67,1:27:13.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:13.71,1:27:13.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:13.77,1:27:13.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:13.82,1:27:13.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:13.85,1:27:13.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:13.86,1:27:13.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:13.89,1:27:13.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:13.90,1:27:13.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:14.14,1:27:16.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Science is, well, it's not very powerful.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:16.52,1:27:16.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:16.82,1:27:22.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, I find it difficult to use the finger and loop technique, so I have been using the
Dialogue: 0,1:27:22.52,1:27:23.90,Default,,0,0,0,,pendulum, so is that acceptable?
Dialogue: 0,1:27:23.90,1:27:24.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:24.32,1:27:26.31,Default,,0,0,0,,The pendulum should give you the same results.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:26.82,1:27:27.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:27.51,1:27:27.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:27.86,1:27:28.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:28.01,1:27:28.59,Default,,0,0,0,,It should be accurate.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:29.05,1:27:29.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:29.14,1:27:33.51,Default,,0,0,0,,The only thing about the pendulum, don't try calibrating things that are obviously evil.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:33.77,1:27:34.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:35.06,1:27:35.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:36.15,1:27:36.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:36.77,1:27:37.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I understand that.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:38.61,1:27:40.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't try calibrating Lucifer or something.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:41.00,1:27:41.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:41.43,1:27:41.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:41.52,1:27:50.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Quantum mechanics, you've said, is in the science, in the intellect level, and then
Dialogue: 0,1:27:50.10,1:27:58.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I came across a body of work by Dr. William Tiller, and he's written Psycho-Energetic Science,
Dialogue: 0,1:27:58.69,1:28:01.96,Default,,0,0,0,,and that calibrates over 500.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:01.96,1:28:02.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Can that be correct?
Dialogue: 0,1:28:02.96,1:28:03.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not catching what you're saying.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:03.96,1:28:04.96,Default,,0,0,0,,She's talking too fast.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:04.96,1:28:05.96,Default,,0,0,0,,She came across this book.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:05.96,1:28:06.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:06.96,1:28:07.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:07.96,1:28:08.96,Default,,0,0,0,,By Tiller.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:08.96,1:28:10.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:10.35,1:28:11.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:11.43,1:28:12.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:12.43,1:28:13.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, Tiller.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:13.43,1:28:14.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:14.43,1:28:15.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Tiller.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:15.64,1:28:16.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:16.64,1:28:17.64,Default,,0,0,0,,And she felt it was in the 500.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:17.64,1:28:20.07,Default,,0,0,0,,She felt that it was ...
Dialogue: 0,1:28:20.07,1:28:21.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't read his name.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:21.07,1:28:22.07,Default,,0,0,0,,What does that say?
Dialogue: 0,1:28:22.07,1:28:23.07,Default,,0,0,0,,William Tiller?
Dialogue: 0,1:28:23.07,1:28:24.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Bill?
Dialogue: 0,1:28:24.07,1:28:25.07,Default,,0,0,0,,William Tiller.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:25.07,1:28:26.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Bill Tiller.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:26.07,1:28:27.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:27.07,1:28:28.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I know Bill.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:28.07,1:28:29.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I've met Bill Tiller.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:29.07,1:28:30.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:30.07,1:28:31.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:31.07,1:28:32.07,Default,,0,0,0,,You want to calibrate this Bill Tiller book?
Dialogue: 0,1:28:32.07,1:28:33.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, please.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:33.17,1:28:34.17,Default,,0,0,0,,This Bill Tiller book is over 540, 580, 575, 560, 565.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:34.17,1:28:35.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Around 560.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:35.27,1:28:36.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:36.27,1:28:37.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I got it right.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:37.27,1:28:38.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I met Bill Tiller.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:38.27,1:28:39.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:39.46,1:28:40.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:40.46,1:28:41.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:41.46,1:28:42.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:42.77,1:28:43.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:43.77,1:28:44.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Bill Tiller.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:44.77,1:28:49.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I had dinner with him two nights ago, and I said, Dr. Tiller, this needs to be put in
Dialogue: 0,1:28:49.02,1:28:53.77,Default,,0,0,0,,a format that it's not esoteric, and he said, it's your job, and he gave it to me.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:53.77,1:28:54.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:54.77,1:28:55.77,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:55.77,1:28:56.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:56.88,1:29:00.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:00.23,1:29:01.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:01.23,1:29:04.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:04.22,1:29:05.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Bill Tiller.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:05.22,1:29:06.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Bill Tiller.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:06.22,1:29:07.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:07.22,1:29:09.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Bill Tiller is well-loved and well-respected and well-known.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:09.02,1:29:13.72,Default,,0,0,0,,First off, I just want to say that I'm honored to be here, and thank you for your wonderful
Dialogue: 0,1:29:13.72,1:29:16.48,Default,,0,0,0,,speech today.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:16.48,1:29:17.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:17.98,1:29:18.98,Default,,0,0,0,,My question is ...
Dialogue: 0,1:29:18.98,1:29:24.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I've learned from you that the mind cannot differentiate between truth and falsehood.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:24.81,1:29:26.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:26.03,1:29:27.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:27.03,1:29:28.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Unaided.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:28.03,1:29:29.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:29.32,1:29:35.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, there are things that I know to be true.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:35.14,1:29:36.14,Default,,0,0,0,,How do I know that?
Dialogue: 0,1:29:36.14,1:29:41.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, you're talking about abstract things, concrete things?
Dialogue: 0,1:29:41.63,1:29:42.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, no, like ...
Dialogue: 0,1:29:42.63,1:29:43.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Like what kind of a thing?
Dialogue: 0,1:29:43.63,1:29:46.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Like, if I run and jump off this stage, I'm going to hit the ground.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:46.63,1:29:47.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:47.63,1:29:49.63,Default,,0,0,0,,That's a linear knowingness of the intellect.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:49.63,1:29:52.72,Default,,0,0,0,,So, if my mind doesn't know that, how do ...
Dialogue: 0,1:29:52.72,1:29:53.72,Default,,0,0,0,,No, your mind is knowing that.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:53.72,1:29:54.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Your intellect is knowing that.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:54.72,1:29:55.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:55.72,1:29:56.76,Default,,0,0,0,,The mind is greater than the intellect.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:56.76,1:29:57.76,Default,,0,0,0,,The intellect is just an instrument, a linear instrument, like an editing machine or a computer.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:57.76,1:29:58.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh-huh.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:58.76,1:29:59.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:59.76,1:30:00.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:00.76,1:30:01.76,Default,,0,0,0,,May I shake your hand, and I'll get a picture, please?
Dialogue: 0,1:30:01.76,1:30:02.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:02.76,1:30:03.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:03.76,1:30:05.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Can I just ask, when you just said 180, were you saying that I calibrated 180?
Dialogue: 0,1:30:05.03,1:30:06.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:06.03,1:30:07.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Just making sure.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:07.03,1:30:08.03,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:08.03,1:30:09.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't say 180.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:09.03,1:30:10.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't say 180.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:10.03,1:30:11.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't say 180.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:11.03,1:30:12.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't say 180.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:12.03,1:30:13.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't say 180.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:13.39,1:30:14.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't say 180.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:14.39,1:30:15.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't say 180.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:15.39,1:30:16.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't say 180.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:16.39,1:30:17.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't say 180.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:17.39,1:30:19.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't say 180.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:19.68,1:30:20.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't say 180.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:20.68,1:30:21.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't say 180.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:21.68,1:30:23.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't say 180.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:23.02,1:30:24.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't say 180.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:24.02,1:30:25.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't say 180.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:25.02,1:30:26.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't say 180.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:26.02,1:30:27.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't say 180.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:27.02,1:30:28.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't say 180.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:28.02,1:30:29.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't say 180.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:29.02,1:30:30.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't say 180.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:30.02,1:30:32.21,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I didn't say 180.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:32.21,1:30:33.21,Default,,0,0,0,,We were calibrating Bill Tiller.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:33.21,1:30:34.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:34.21,1:30:35.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I must have been mistaken.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:35.21,1:30:36.94,Default,,0,0,0,,It was fine.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:36.94,1:30:37.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:37.94,1:30:39.14,Default,,0,0,0,,We did Bill Tiller, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:39.14,1:30:40.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:40.14,1:30:42.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:42.84,1:30:43.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:43.84,1:30:44.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, you're safe.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:45.84,1:30:47.92,Default,,0,0,0,,If you're a nut job, I'd find a way to avoid you.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:48.92,1:30:50.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,1:30:50.68,1:30:51.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello, Dr. Hawkins.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:51.68,1:30:57.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:57.30,1:30:58.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Here's a gift for you that is a gift that's coming to you.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:58.30,1:30:59.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to give it to you.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:59.30,1:31:00.30,Default,,0,0,0,,You're going to give it to me.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:00.30,1:31:02.97,Default,,0,0,0,,is from Ramana Maharshi's cave
Dialogue: 0,1:31:02.97,1:31:05.53,Default,,0,0,0,,and I'd like you to accept it.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:05.53,1:31:05.77,Default,,0,0,0,,It's what?
Dialogue: 0,1:31:07.10,1:31:08.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Ramana Maharshi's cave
Dialogue: 0,1:31:08.81,1:31:10.38,Default,,0,0,0,,and I'd like you to accept it.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:10.38,1:31:11.06,Default,,0,0,0,,It's from what?
Dialogue: 0,1:31:12.46,1:31:13.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Maharshi?
Dialogue: 0,1:31:13.93,1:31:14.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Cave?
Dialogue: 0,1:31:14.84,1:31:16.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, cave.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:17.13,1:31:18.97,Default,,0,0,0,,It's some Vibhuti
Dialogue: 0,1:31:18.97,1:31:21.09,Default,,0,0,0,,from some holy ash.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:21.09,1:31:22.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Now I know what you're saying.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:22.25,1:31:24.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, from Ramana Maharshi's cave.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:24.01,1:31:24.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:24.94,1:31:26.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd like to thank you so much
Dialogue: 0,1:31:26.44,1:31:27.86,Default,,0,0,0,,for what you've done in my life.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:28.01,1:31:29.52,Default,,0,0,0,,It's been just amazing.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:30.75,1:31:32.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I have a conundrum
Dialogue: 0,1:31:32.25,1:31:33.71,Default,,0,0,0,,and it's regarding the turban.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:34.17,1:31:35.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been using the turban
Dialogue: 0,1:31:35.82,1:31:37.89,Default,,0,0,0,,as a source of protection
Dialogue: 0,1:31:37.89,1:31:40.47,Default,,0,0,0,,for the last 18 months
Dialogue: 0,1:31:40.47,1:31:42.67,Default,,0,0,0,,dealing with addictions
Dialogue: 0,1:31:42.67,1:31:46.59,Default,,0,0,0,,and mostly stemming from the gay scene.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:47.35,1:31:48.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Mostly stemming from what?
Dialogue: 0,1:31:48.75,1:31:49.60,Default,,0,0,0,,The gay scene.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:51.30,1:31:52.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, G-A-Y?
Dialogue: 0,1:31:52.56,1:31:52.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Gay.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:53.02,1:31:54.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, oh, oh, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:54.07,1:31:54.89,Default,,0,0,0,,The gay scene.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:55.46,1:31:58.46,Default,,0,0,0,,And I'm questioning from your teachings
Dialogue: 0,1:31:58.46,1:32:01.10,Default,,0,0,0,,and from my own ego dramas
Dialogue: 0,1:32:01.10,1:32:01.50,Default,,0,0,0,,whether,
Dialogue: 0,1:32:01.52,1:32:03.27,Default,,0,0,0,,whether it's necessary anymore
Dialogue: 0,1:32:03.27,1:32:05.02,Default,,0,0,0,,and whether I should continue or not,
Dialogue: 0,1:32:05.02,1:32:07.07,Default,,0,0,0,,although it's been very helpful.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:07.07,1:32:07.92,Default,,0,0,0,,And I'm wondering.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:07.92,1:32:08.76,Default,,0,0,0,,To wear the turban,
Dialogue: 0,1:32:08.76,1:32:09.60,Default,,0,0,0,,is that the question?
Dialogue: 0,1:32:09.60,1:32:10.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:10.60,1:32:11.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:11.50,1:32:13.14,Default,,0,0,0,,It's helpful for him to continue
Dialogue: 0,1:32:13.14,1:32:15.31,Default,,0,0,0,,to wear the turban.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:15.31,1:32:17.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, it's a reminder of your commitment.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:17.68,1:32:19.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:19.06,1:32:20.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you so much.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:20.19,1:32:21.73,Default,,0,0,0,,May I touch your feet, please?
Dialogue: 0,1:32:21.73,1:32:22.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:22.57,1:32:23.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:23.39,1:32:25.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, it's a reminder of your commitment.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:25.31,1:32:26.89,Default,,0,0,0,,And it's a difficult one you've made
Dialogue: 0,1:32:26.89,1:32:29.93,Default,,0,0,0,,to transcend that kind of a lifestyle.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:29.93,1:32:31.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Very hard, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:31.39,1:32:32.48,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a hard one to make.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:32.48,1:32:34.25,Default,,0,0,0,,So, you need all the help you can get.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:34.25,1:32:36.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, Dr.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:36.11,1:32:36.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:36.81,1:32:43.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, it's someone's purse.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:43.53,1:32:50.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't like their purse.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:50.22,1:32:51.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Me aqua tasen.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:51.39,1:32:54.38,Default,,0,0,0,,And it means all my relations, we are all related.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:54.38,1:32:55.88,Default,,0,0,0,,And so, I thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:55.88,1:32:56.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:56.47,1:32:58.53,Default,,0,0,0,,For this time.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:58.53,1:33:01.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I walk a very strong spiritual walk.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:01.92,1:33:04.64,Default,,0,0,0,,And I had a great deal of resistance coming here.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:04.64,1:33:07.02,Default,,0,0,0,,This is my first time I've ever saw you.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:07.02,1:33:09.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I've read your book, Power Versus Force.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:09.96,1:33:11.89,Default,,0,0,0,,And I had resistance coming here because I
Dialogue: 0,1:33:11.89,1:33:13.47,Default,,0,0,0,,walk directly with spirit as its guide.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:13.47,1:33:16.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Spirit said, you must go.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:16.23,1:33:17.61,Default,,0,0,0,,It's imperative that you go.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:17.61,1:33:19.30,Default,,0,0,0,,And so, I want to thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:19.30,1:33:20.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm full of gratitude.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:20.85,1:33:21.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:21.35,1:33:23.50,Default,,0,0,0,,What you spoke about today, spirit
Dialogue: 0,1:33:23.50,1:33:26.18,Default,,0,0,0,,has taught me many, many years of this.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:26.18,1:33:28.11,Default,,0,0,0,,And so, it's a great confirmation for me.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:28.11,1:33:31.81,Default,,0,0,0,,And so, I'm very grateful to you and full of gratitude.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:31.81,1:33:33.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:33.02,1:33:37.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, the question, which I have great resistance of asking.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:37.06,1:33:38.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, you don't have to ask it.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:38.27,1:33:38.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I do.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:42.30,1:33:43.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I do.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:43.02,1:33:43.73,Default,,0,0,0,,They keep insisting.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:43.73,1:33:44.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I ask.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:44.50,1:33:49.84,Default,,0,0,0,,And the question is, how do you walk the strings of time?
Dialogue: 0,1:33:49.84,1:33:50.69,Default,,0,0,0,,How do you what?
Dialogue: 0,1:33:50.69,1:33:53.56,Default,,0,0,0,,How do you walk the strings of time?
Dialogue: 0,1:33:53.56,1:33:54.56,Default,,0,0,0,,And do you understand this?
Dialogue: 0,1:33:54.56,1:33:55.76,Default,,0,0,0,,There aren't any strings of time.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:55.76,1:33:57.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:57.15,1:33:58.23,Default,,0,0,0,,OK, I needed to know that.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:58.23,1:33:59.30,Default,,0,0,0,,It's all in your head.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:59.30,1:34:00.10,Default,,0,0,0,,OK.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:00.10,1:34:01.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I needed to know that.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:01.11,1:34:01.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:01.76,1:34:03.88,Default,,0,0,0,,And then, how do you learn?
Dialogue: 0,1:34:03.88,1:34:06.39,Default,,0,0,0,,And there's been several times, three times in my life
Dialogue: 0,1:34:06.39,1:34:09.15,Default,,0,0,0,,that I've disappeared in front of people.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:09.15,1:34:11.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't know how I did that.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:11.02,1:34:12.60,Default,,0,0,0,,What's that about?
Dialogue: 0,1:34:12.60,1:34:13.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I have no idea.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:13.84,1:34:17.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Like, I swear, physically, they were standing right in front of me,
Dialogue: 0,1:34:17.76,1:34:19.46,Default,,0,0,0,,and they didn't see me.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:19.46,1:34:21.10,Default,,0,0,0,,So, I don't understand that.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:21.10,1:34:22.47,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't understand that?
Dialogue: 0,1:34:22.47,1:34:24.80,Default,,0,0,0,,No, but I could with a little research, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:24.80,1:34:26.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Could you?
Dialogue: 0,1:34:26.72,1:34:27.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you teasing me?
Dialogue: 0,1:34:38.81,1:34:41.68,Default,,0,0,0,,They didn't notice you.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:41.68,1:34:43.60,Default,,0,0,0,,They didn't notice her.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:43.60,1:34:44.94,Default,,0,0,0,,They didn't notice you.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:44.94,1:34:46.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I was standing right in front of them.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:46.06,1:34:47.25,Default,,0,0,0,,They were interested in something else.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:47.25,1:34:48.94,Default,,0,0,0,,You were boring, so they looked elsewhere.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:48.94,1:34:49.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:49.44,1:34:49.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:53.78,1:34:55.02,Default,,0,0,0,,You're a blessing to me.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:55.02,1:34:57.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:57.71,1:34:59.17,Default,,0,0,0,,No explanation.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:59.17,1:35:00.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:00.10,1:35:02.40,Default,,0,0,0,,It's happened three times, and it was really befuddling to me,
Dialogue: 0,1:35:02.40,1:35:04.56,Default,,0,0,0,,and I wasn't quite sure what that was about.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:04.56,1:35:05.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:05.48,1:35:06.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I can see what you mean.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:06.60,1:35:07.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:07.10,1:35:07.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:07.97,1:35:08.94,Default,,0,0,0,,You're a blessing.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:08.94,1:35:11.17,Default,,0,0,0,,You wondered if you became invisible for a few minutes.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:11.17,1:35:11.78,Default,,0,0,0,,What was happening?
Dialogue: 0,1:35:11.78,1:35:12.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:12.28,1:35:17.02,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll take one more, and then we'll continue.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:17.02,1:35:20.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello, Doc.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:20.02,1:35:21.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello, Doc.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:21.03,1:35:22.03,Default,,0,0,0,,You want something signed?
Dialogue: 0,1:35:22.03,1:35:23.56,Default,,0,0,0,,And Susan.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:23.56,1:35:24.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:24.80,1:35:25.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:25.14,1:35:25.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Gosh.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:25.64,1:35:27.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you so much.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:27.46,1:35:28.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, indeed.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:28.27,1:35:30.39,Default,,0,0,0,,And please may I have your blessing?
Dialogue: 0,1:35:30.39,1:35:32.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:32.86,1:35:33.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:33.86,1:35:34.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:34.56,1:35:36.72,Default,,0,0,0,,God bless you.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:36.72,1:35:37.82,Default,,0,0,0,,God bless you.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:37.82,1:35:42.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Coming from this side.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:42.96,1:35:43.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Dubai.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:43.50,1:35:44.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Dubai.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:44.00,1:35:46.98,Default,,0,0,0,,OK.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:46.98,1:35:53.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Everybody and his brother's in Dubai nowadays.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:53.18,1:35:57.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Next thing you know, we'll have to go to Dubai, for God's sake.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:57.02,1:35:57.52,Default,,0,0,0,,OK.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:57.52,1:35:58.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I think that's exactly it.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:58.82,1:36:02.68,Default,,0,0,0,,One more?
Dialogue: 0,1:36:02.68,1:36:03.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that it?
Dialogue: 0,1:36:03.18,1:36:03.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Run.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:03.68,1:36:04.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Run, Rabbit.
